                    81
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    82
                    
                    
                      
        ## Get minumimum length for when EXSTDTC and EXENDTC are different lengths

                    		
                  

                  

                    83
                    5x
                    
                      
        df$startdtc = ifelse(!is_sas_na(df$EXSTDTC),

                    		
                  

                  

                    84
                    5x
                    
                      
                             substr(df$EXSTDTC, 1, pmin(nchar(df$EXSTDTC), nchar(df$EXENDTC), na.rm = TRUE)),

                    		
                  

                  

                    85
                    5x
                    
                      
                             df$EXSTDTC)

                    		
                  

                  

                    86
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    87
                    5x
                    
                      
        df$startdtc = ifelse(is_sas_na(df$EXENDTC),

                    		
                  

                  

                    88
                    5x
                    
                      
                             substr(df$EXSTDTC, 1, pmin(nchar(df$EXSTDTC), nchar(df$EXSTDTC), na.rm = TRUE)),

                    		
                  

                  

                    89
                    5x
                    
                      
                             df$EXSTDTC)

                    		
                  

                  

                    90
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    91
                    5x
                    
                      
        df$enddtc = ifelse(!is_sas_na(df$EXENDTC),

                    		
                  

                  

                    92
                    5x
                    
                      
                           substr(df$EXENDTC, 1, pmin(nchar(df$EXSTDTC), nchar(df$EXENDTC), na.rm = TRUE)),

                    		
                  

                  

                    93
                    5x
                    
                      
                           df$EXENDTC)

                    		
                  

                  

                    94
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    95
                    5x
                    
                      
        df$enddtc = ifelse(is_sas_na(df$EXSTDTC),

                    		
                  

                  

                    96
                    5x
                    
                      
                           substr(df$EXENDTC, 1, pmin(nchar(df$EXENDTC), nchar(df$EXENDTC), na.rm = TRUE)),

                    		
                  

                  

                    97
                    5x
                    
                      
                           df$EXENDTC)

                    		
                  

                  

                    98
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    99
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    100
                    5x
                    
                      
        df$startdate = substr(df$startdtc, 1, 10)

                    		
                  

                  

                    101
                    5x
                    
                      
        df$enddate   = substr(df$enddtc, 1, 10)

                    		
                  

                  

                    102
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    103
                    5x
                    
                      
        df$starttime = substr(df$startdtc, 12, 19)

                    		
                  

                  

                    104
                    5x
                    
                      
        df$endtime   = substr(df$enddtc, 12, 19)

                    		
                  

                  

                    105
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    106
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    107
                    
                    
                      
        # convert string to date/time

                    		
                  

                  

                    108
                    5x
                    
                      
        df$DT1 = NA

                    		
                  

                  

                    109
                    5x
                    
                      
        df$DT1[nchar(df$startdate) == 10] <- as.POSIXct(df$startdate[nchar(df$startdate) == 10], format = "%Y-%m-%d")

                    		
                  

                  

                    110
                    5x
                    
                      
        df$DT1[nchar(df$startdate) == 7]  <- as.POSIXct(df$startdate[nchar(df$startdate) == 7], format = "%Y-%M")

                    		
                  

                  

                    111
                    5x
                    
                      
        df$DT1[nchar(df$startdate) == 4]  <- as.POSIXct(df$startdate[nchar(df$startdate)== 4], format = "%Y")

                    		
                  

                  

                    112
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    113
                    5x
                    
                      
        df$DT2 = NA

                    		
                  

                  

                    114
                    5x
                    
                      
        df$DT2[nchar(df$enddate) == 10] <- as.POSIXct(df$enddate[nchar(df$enddate) == 10], format = "%Y-%m-%d")

                    		
                  

                  

                    115
                    5x
                    
                      
        df$DT2[nchar(df$enddate) == 7]  <- as.POSIXct(df$enddate[nchar(df$enddate) == 7], format = "%Y-%M")

                    		
                  

                  

                    116
                    5x
                    
                      
        df$DT2[nchar(df$enddate) == 4]  <- as.POSIXct(df$enddate[nchar(df$enddate) == 4], format = "%Y")

                    		
                  

                  

                    117
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    118
                    5x
                    
                      
        df$TM1 = NA

                    		
                  

                  

                    119
                    5x
                    
                      
        df$TM1[nchar(df$starttime) == 8] <- as.POSIXct(df$starttime[nchar(df$starttime) == 8], format = "%H:%M:%S")

                    		
                  

                  

                    120
                    5x
                    
                      
        df$TM1[nchar(df$starttime) == 5] <- as.POSIXct(df$starttime[nchar(df$starttime) == 5], format = "%H:%M")

                    		
                  

                  

                    121
                    5x
                    
                      
        df$TM1[nchar(df$starttime) == 2] <- as.POSIXct(df$starttime[nchar(df$starttime)==2], format = "%H")

                    		
                  

                  

                    122
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    123
                    5x
                    
                      
        df$TM2 = NA

                    5x
                    
                      
        df$TM2[nchar(df$endtime)==8] <- as.POSIXct(df$endtime[nchar(df$endtime) == 8], format = "%H:%M:%S")

                    		
                  

                  

                    125
                    5x
                    
                      
        df$TM2[nchar(df$endtime)==5] <- as.POSIXct(df$endtime[nchar(df$endtime) == 5], format = "%H:%M")

                    		
                  

                  

                    126
                    5x
                    
                      
        df$TM2[nchar(df$endtime)==2] <- as.POSIXct(df$endtime[nchar(df$endtime) == 2], format = "%H")

                    		
                  

                  

                    127
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    128
                    
                    
                      
        # Include VISIT and EXOCCUR in display if they exist in the data set

                    		
                  

                  

                    129
                    5x
                    
                      
        myvars = c("USUBJID", "EXTRT", "EXSTDTC", "EXENDTC")

                    		
                  

                  

                    130
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    131
                    5x
                    
                      
        if (EX %has_any% "VISIT") {

                    		
                  

                  

                    132
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    133
                    5x
                    
                      
            myvars = c(myvars, "VISIT")

                    		
                  

                  

                    134
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    135
                    
                    
                      
        }

                    		
                  

                  

                    136
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    137
                    
                    
                      
        # Start date/time after end date/time, including missing start/end dates

                    		
                  

                  

                    138
                    
                    
                      
        # Create issue flag types

                    		
                  

                  

                    139
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    140
                    
                    
                      
        # filter records where route is intravenous

                    		
                  

                  

                    141
                    5x
                    
                      
        mydf0 <- subset(df, grepl("INTRAVENOUS", toupper(df$EXROUTE)))

                    		
                  

                  

                    142
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    143
                    
                    
                      
        # create check flags for date checks

                    		
                  

                  

                    144
                    5x
                    
                      
        mydf1 <- mydf0

                    		
                  

                  

                    145
                    5x
                    
                      
        mydf1$check_stat <- case_when(

                    		
                  

                  

                    146
                    5x
                    
                      
            mydf0$DT1 != mydf0$DT2 & is_sas_na(mydf0$TM1) & is_sas_na(mydf0$TM2) ~ "Different Start/End date for Infusion",

                    		
                  

                  

                    147
                    5x
                    
                      
            !is_sas_na(mydf0$DT1) & is_sas_na(mydf0$TM1) & is_sas_na(mydf0$EXENDTC) ~ "Missing End date",

                    		
                  

                  

                    148
                    5x
                    
                      
            !is_sas_na(mydf0$DT2) & is_sas_na(mydf0$TM2) & is_sas_na(mydf0$EXSTDTC) ~ "Missing Start date",

                    		
                  

                  

                    149
                    5x
                    
                      
            TRUE ~ ""

                    		
                  

                  

                    150
                    
                    
                      
        )

                    		
                  

                  

                    151
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    152
                    
                    
                      
        # filter empty check flags

                    		
                  

                  

                    153
                    5x
                    
                      
        mydf1 <- select(mydf1, all_of(myvars), check_stat) %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    154
                    5x
                    
                      
            filter(check_stat != "")

                    		
                  

                  

                    155
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    156
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    157
                    
                    
                      
        # create check flags for date and time checks

                    		
                  

                  

                    158
                    5x
                    
                      
        mydf2 <- mydf0

                    		
                  

                  

                    159
                    5x
                    
                      
        mydf2$check_stat <- case_when(

                    		
                  

                  

                    160
                    5x
                    
                      
            mydf0$DT1 == mydf0$DT2 & mydf0$TM1 > mydf0$TM2 ~ "Same Start/End date but Start time after End time",

                    		
                  

                  

                    161
                    5x
                    
                      
            mydf0$DT1 != mydf0$DT2 & !is_sas_na(mydf0$TM1) & !is_sas_na(mydf0$TM2) ~ "Different Start/End date for Infusion",

                    		
                  

                  

                    162
                    5x
                    
                      
            !is_sas_na(mydf0$DT1) & !is_sas_na(mydf0$TM1) & is_sas_na(mydf0$EXENDTC) ~ "Missing End date/time",

                    		
                  

                  

                    163
                    5x
                    
                      
            !is_sas_na(mydf0$DT2) & !is_sas_na(mydf0$TM2) & is_sas_na(mydf0$EXSTDTC) ~ "Missing Start date/time",

                    		
                  

                  

                    164
                    5x
                    
                      
            TRUE ~ ""

                    		
                  

                  

                    165
                    
                    
                      
        )

                    		
                  

                  

                    166

check_ex_exstdtc_after_exendtc <- function(EX){

                    		
                  

                  

                    43
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    44
                    
                    
                      
  ###First check that required variables exist and return a message if they don't

                    		
                  

                  

                    45
                    8x

                    46
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    47
                    !

                    48
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    49

                    52
                    7x

                    53
                    7x
                    
                      
      EX$enddate=substr(EX$EXENDTC,1, pmin(nchar(EX$EXSTDTC),nchar(EX$EXENDTC),na.rm = TRUE))

                    55

                    7x

                    7x

                    7x

                    65
                    7x
                    
                      
      EX$DT1[nchar(EX$startdate)==4] <- as.POSIXct(EX$startdate[nchar(EX$startdate)==4],format="%Y")

                    		
                  

                  

                    66
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    67
                    7x
                    
                      
      EX$DT2 = NA

                    		
                  

                  

                    68
                    7x
                    
                      
      EX$DT2[nchar(EX$enddate)==16] <- as.POSIXct(EX$enddate[nchar(EX$enddate)==16],format="%Y-%m-%dT%H:%M")

                    		
                  

                  

                    69
                    7x
                    
                      
      EX$DT2[nchar(EX$enddate)==13] <- as.POSIXct(EX$enddate[nchar(EX$enddate)==13],format="%Y-%m-%dT%H")

                    		
                  

                  

                    70
                    7x
                    
                      
      EX$DT2[nchar(EX$enddate)==10] <- as.POSIXct(EX$enddate[nchar(EX$enddate)==10],format="%Y-%m-%d")

                    		
                  

                  

                    71
                    7x
                    
                      
      EX$DT2[nchar(EX$enddate)==7] <- as.POSIXct(EX$enddate[nchar(EX$enddate)==7],format="%Y-%M")

                    		
                  

                  

                    72
                    7x
                    
                      
      EX$DT2[nchar(EX$enddate)==4] <- as.POSIXct(EX$enddate[nchar(EX$enddate)==4],format="%Y")

check_ae_aestdtc_after_aeendtc <- function(AE,preproc=identity,...){

                    		
                  

                  

                    44
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    45
                    
                    
                      
  ###First check that required variables exist and return a message if they don't

                    		
                  

                  

                    46
                    8x

                    47
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    48
                    1x
                    
                      
      fail(lacks_msg(AE, c("USUBJID", "AETERM", "AEDECOD", "AESTDTC", "AEENDTC")))

                    		
                  

                  

                    49
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    50

                    51

    #Apply company specific preprocessing function

                    		
                  

                  

                    53
                    6x
                    
                      
    AE = preproc(AE,...)

                    57
                    6x

                    58
                    6x
                    
                      
      AE$enddate=substr(AE$AEENDTC,1, pmin(nchar(AE$AESTDTC),nchar(AE$AEENDTC),na.rm = TRUE))

                    6x

                    6x

                    67
                    6x
                    
                      
      AE$DT1[nchar(AE$startdate)==13] <- as.POSIXct(AE$startdate[nchar(AE$startdate)==13],format="%Y-%m-%dT%H")

                    		
                  

                  

                    68
                    6x

                    69
                    6x
                    
                      
      AE$DT1[nchar(AE$startdate)==7] <- as.POSIXct(AE$startdate[nchar(AE$startdate)==7],format="%Y-%M")

                    		
                  

                  

                    70
                    6x
                    
                      
      AE$DT1[nchar(AE$startdate)==4] <- as.POSIXct(AE$startdate[nchar(AE$startdate)==4],format="%Y")

                    		
                  

                  

                    71
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    72
                    6x
                    
                      
      AE$DT2 = NA

                    6x

                    74
                    6x
                    
                      
      AE$DT2[nchar(AE$enddate)==13] <- as.POSIXct(AE$enddate[nchar(AE$enddate)==13],format="%Y-%m-%dT%H")

                    6x

                    76
                    6x

                    77
                    6x

      filter(!is_sas_na(AESTDTC) & !is_sas_na(AEENDTC) & (DT1 > DT2 )) %>%

                    6x
                    
                      
      select(any_of(c("USUBJID", "AETERM", "AEDECOD", "AESTDTC", "AEENDTC","RAVE")))

                    		
                  

                  

                    83
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    84
                    6x
                    
                      
    rownames(mydf)=NULL

                    		
                  

                  

                    85
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    86
                    
                    
                      
    ### Return message if no records with issue

                    		
                  

                  

                    87
                    6x
                    
                      
    if(nrow(mydf)==0){

                    		
                  

                  

                    88
                    3x
                    
                      
     pass()

                    92
                    3x

                    121
                    
                    
                      
## Note, in a case where both AETOXGR and AESEV exist and some records are supposed to have AETOXGR populated while others have AESEV (ie mutaually exlusive)

                    		
                  

                  

                    122
                    
                    
                      
## Then this check will likely return false positives as it expects a variable to be populated for all records

                    		
                  

                  

                    123
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    124
                    
                    
                      
check_ae_fatal <- function(AE,preproc=identity,...){

                    		
                  

                  

                    125
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    126
                    
                    
                      
  ###First check that required variables exist and return a message if they don't

                    		
                  

                  

                    127
                    9x
                    
                      
  if(AE %lacks_any% c("USUBJID", "AEDECOD", "AESTDTC","AEDTHDTC", "AEOUT", "AESDTH")){

                    		
                  

                  

                    128
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    129
                    !
                    
                      
      fail(lacks_msg(AE, c("USUBJID", "AEDECOD", "AESTDTC", "AEDTHDTC", "AEOUT", "AESDTH")))

                    		
                  

                  

                    130
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    131
                    
                    
                      
  } else{

                    		
                  

                  

                    132
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    133
                    
                    
                      
    #Apply company specific preprocessing function

                    		
                  

                  

                    134
                    8x
                    
                      
    AE = preproc(AE,...)

                    		
                  

                  

                    135
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    136
                    8x
                    
                      
    outlist=list() #empty list for results

                    		
                  

                  

                    137
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    138
                    
                    
                      
    # check if AEOUT=='FATAL' that there is a corresponding AEDTHDTC, death date

                    		
                  

                  

                    139
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    140
                    8x
                    
                      
    if(AE %has_any% "AETOXGR" & !all(is_sas_na(AE$AETOXGR))){ #Non-empty AETOXGR exists

                    		
                  

                  

                    141
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    142
                    7x
                    
                      
    outlist[[1]] = AE %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    143
                    7x
                    
                      
      filter(AEOUT=='FATAL' & (is_sas_na(AEDTHDTC) | AETOXGR !=5 | is_sas_na(AETOXGR) | AESDTH != "Y" | is_sas_na(AESDTH)))

                    		
                  

                  

                    144
                    
                    
                      
    }

                    		
                  

                  

                    145
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    146
                    8x
                    
                      
    if(AE %has_any% "AESEV" & !all(is_sas_na(AE$AESEV))){ #Non-empty AESEV exists

                    		
                  

                  

                    147
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    148
                    !
                    
                      
    outlist[[2]] <- AE %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    149
                    !
                    
                      
          filter(AEOUT=='FATAL' & (is_sas_na(AEDTHDTC) | AESEV != "SEVERE" | AESDTH != "Y" | is_sas_na(AESDTH)))

                    		
                  

                  

                    150
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    151

                    152
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    153

                    154

                    155
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    156
                    8x
                    
                      
    if(!(AE %has_any% "AESEV" & !all(is_sas_na(AE$AESEV))) & !(AE %has_any% "AETOXGR" & !all(is_sas_na(AE$AETOXGR)))){

                    		
                  

                  

                    157
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    158
                    1x
                    
                      
    outlist[[3]] <- AE %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    159
                    1x
                    
                      
          filter(AEOUT=='FATAL' & (is_sas_na(AEDTHDTC) | AESDTH != "Y" | is_sas_na(AESDTH)))

                    		
                  

                  

                    160
                    
                    
                      
    }

                    		
                  

                  

                    161
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    162
                    8x
                    
                      
    mydf = bind_rows(outlist)

                    		
                  

                  

                    163
                    
                    
                      
    # leave only variables on which we want to check for fatalities and their corresponding death dates

                    		
                  

                  

                    164
                    8x
                    
                      
    mydf = unique(mydf[,intersect(names(AE),c("STUDYID","USUBJID", "AEDECOD", "AESTDTC","AEDTHDTC", "AEOUT","AESEV","AETOXGR","AESDTH","RAVE"))])

                    		
                  

                  

                    165
                    8x
                    
                      
    rownames(mydf)=NULL

                    		
                  

                  

                    166
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    167
                    
                    
                      
    ### Return message if no inconsistency between AEOUT and AEDTHDTC

                    		
                  

                  

                    168
                    8x
                    
                      
    if(nrow(mydf)==0){

                    		
                  

                  

                    169
                    4x
                    
                      
      pass()

                    		
                  

                  

                    170
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    171
                    
                    
                      
      ### Return subset dataframe if there are records with inconsistency

                    		
                  

                  

                    172
                    4x
                    
                      
    }else if(nrow(mydf)>0){

                    		
                  

                  

                    173
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    174
                    4x
                    
                      
      fail(paste("AE has ",length(unique(mydf$USUBJID))," patient(s) with AE death variable inconsistencies when outcome marked FATAL. ",sep=""), mydf)

#' @title Check that all EX start dates are earlier than last

check_ex_exstdtc_visit_ordinal_error <- function(EX){

                    		
                  

                  

                    41
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    42
                    4x
                    
                      
    class(EX) <- 'data.frame'

                    		
                  

                  

                    43
                    4x
                    
                      
    vars = c("USUBJID", "EXTRT", "VISITNUM", "VISIT", "EXSTDTC")

                    		
                  

                  

                    44
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    45
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    46
                    
                    
                      
    ### First check that required variables exist and return a message if they don't

                    		
                  

                  

                    47
                    4x
                    
                      
    if (EX %lacks_any% vars) {

                    		
                  

                  

                    48
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    49
                    !
                    
                      
        fail(lacks_msg(EX, vars))

                    		
                  

                  

                    50
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    51
                    
                    
                      
    ### Dont run if VISITNUM is all missing

                    		
                  

                  

                    52
                    4x
                    
                      
    } else if (length(unique(EX[["VISITNUM"]]))<=1) {

                    		
                  

                  

                    53
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    54
                    !
                    
                      
        fail(msg="VISITNUM exists but only a single value")

                    		
                  

                  

                    55
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    56
                    
                    
                      
    } else {

                    		
                  

                  

                    57
                    !
                    
                      
        if ("EXOCCUR" %in% names(EX)) { EX <- subset(EX,EX$EXOCCUR == "Y",)}

                    		
                  

                  

                    58
                    4x
                    
                      
        mydf2 <- dtc_dupl_early(dts = subset(EX,!grepl("UNSCHEDU",toupper(EX$VISIT)),), vars = vars,

                    		
                  

                  

                    59
                    
                    
                      
                                ### groupby variables used for grouping and visit.order derivation

                    		
                  

                  

                    60
                    4x
                    
                      
                                groupby = vars[c(1, 2)],

                    		
                  

                  

                    61
                    4x
                    
                      
                                dtc = vars[5],

                    		
                  

                  

                    62
                    
                    
                      
                                ### variables used for ordering before visit.order derivation

                    		
                  

                  

                    63

                    6x

                    6x

                    1x

                    6x

                    108

                    5x

check_oe_bcva_tot_mismatch <- function(OE) {

                    		
                  

                  

                    92
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    93
                    6x
                    
                      
    if (OE %lacks_any% c("USUBJID", "OETESTCD", "OECAT", "OESCAT", "OETSTDTL", "OESTRESN",  "OELAT", "VISIT",  "OEDTC")) {

                    		
                  

                  

                    94
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    95
                    1x
                    
                      
        fail(lacks_msg(OE, c("USUBJID", "OETESTCD", "OECAT", "OESCAT", "OETSTDTL", "OESTRESN",  "OELAT", "VISIT",  "OEDTC")))

                    		
                  

                  

                    96

check_ts_aedict <- function(TS){

                    		
                  

                  

                    69
                    
                    
                      
    ###First check that required variables exist and return a message if they don't

                    		
                  

                  

                    70
                    9x
                    
                      
    if(TS %lacks_any% c("TSPARMCD", "TSVAL")){

                    		
                  

                  

                    71
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    72
                    1x
                    
                      
        fail(lacks_msg(TS, c("TSPARMCD", "TSVAL")))

                    		
                  

                  

                    73
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    74
                    
                    
                      
    }else{

                    		
                  

                  

                    75
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    76
                    
                    
                      
        ### identify current MedDRA version

                    		
                  

                  

                    77
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    78
                    8x
                    
                      
        t <-  Sys.Date()

                    		
                  

                  

                    79
                    8x
                    
                      
        y <-  substring(t,1,4)

                    		
                  

                  

                    80
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    81
                    8x
                    
                      
        may <- seq(as.Date(paste0(y, "-05-01")),as.Date(paste0(y, "-05-07")),by="1 day")

                    		
                  

                  

                    82
                    8x
                    
                      
        date1 <-  may[weekdays(may) == "Monday"]

                    		
                  

                  

                    83
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    84
                    8x
                    
                      
        nov <- seq(as.Date(paste0(y, "-11-01")),as.Date(paste0(y, "-11-07")),by="1 day")

                    		
                  

                  

                    85
                    8x
                    
                      
        date2 <- nov[weekdays(nov) == "Monday"]

                    		
                  

                  

                    86
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    87
                    
                    
                      
        # Work out the main MedDRA version of the year; start on version 24.0

                    		
                  

                  

                    88
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    89
                    8x
                    
                      
        meddra_version <- as.numeric(y) - 2021 + 24

                    		
                  

                  

                    90
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    91
                    
                    
                      
        # if today is before the first Monday of May, MedDRA version is the previous version, eg 23.1

                    		
                  

                  

                    92
                    
                    
                      
        # if today is after the first Monday of November, MedDRA version is the next version, eg 24.1

                    		
                  

                  

                    93
                    8x
                    
                      
        meddra_version_num <- case_when(t < date1 ~ as.character(meddra_version - 0.9),

                    		
                  

                  

                    94
                    8x
                    
                      
                                        t >= date1 & t< date2 ~ paste0(meddra_version, ".0"),

                    		
                  

                  

                    95
                    8x
                    
                      
                                        t >= date2 ~ as.character(meddra_version + 0.1))

                    		
                  

                  

                    96
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    97
                    
                    
                      
        ### Subset TS to only AEDICT record

                    		
                  

                  

                    98
                    8x
                    
                      
        mydf <- subset(TS, TS$TSPARMCD=="AEDICT", c("TSPARMCD","TSVAL"))

                    		
                  

                  

                    99
                    
                    
                      
        ###Print to report

                    		
                  

                  

                    100
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    101
                    
                    
                      
        ### Pass if MedDRA version is populated

                    		
                  

                  

                    102
                    8x
                    
                      
        if (nrow(mydf) == 1) {

                    		
                  

                  

                    103
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    104
                    
                    
                      
            ###Adding calculated MedDRA Version so it is included in the dataframe that is returned if the check fails

                    		
                  

                  

                    105
                    6x
                    
                      
            mydf <- mydf %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    106
                    6x
                    
                      
                mutate(Current_MedDRA_version = meddra_version_num)

                    		
                  

                  

                    107
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    108
                    6x
                    
                      
            meddra=mydf %>% select(TSVAL) %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    109
                    6x
                    
                      
                pull() %>% trimws()

                    		
                  

                  

                    110
                    6x
                    
                      
            meddra_short <- substr(meddra,nchar(as.character(meddra))-3,nchar(as.character(meddra)))

                    		
                  

                  

                    111
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    112
                    6x
                    
                      
            if (is_sas_na(meddra)) {

                    		
                  

                  

                    113
                    2x
                    
                      
                fail("No value in TS.TSVAL where TS.TSPARMCD=AEDICT.", mydf)

                    		
                  

                  

                    114
                    
                    
                      
            }

                    		
                  

                  

                    115
                    4x
                    
                      
            else if(meddra_short != meddra_version_num){

                    		
                  

                  

                    116
                    3x
                    
                      
                fail(paste("MedDRA version in TS.TSVAL where TS.TSPARMCD=AEDICT is not the latest version as of",Sys.Date()), mydf)

                    		
                  

                  

                    117
                    
                    
                      
            }

                    		
                  

                  

                    118
                    
                    
                      
            else {

                    		
                  

                  

                    119
                    1x
                    
                      
                if (grepl("MEDDRA", toupper(mydf$TSVAL), ignore.case=TRUE)) {

                    		
                  

                  

                    120
                    1x
                    
                      
                    pass()

                    		
                  

                  

                    121
                    
                    
                      
                } else {

                    		
                  

                  

                    122
                    !
                    
                      
                    fail("The string 'MedDRA' not found in TS.TSVAL where TS.TSPARMCD=AEDICT.", mydf)

                    		
                  

                  

                    123
                    
                    
                      
                }

                    		
                  

                  

                    124
                    
                    
                      
            }

                    		
                  

                  

                    125
                    
                    
                      
            ### Return message if MedDRA version is not populated in TS or multiple records

                    		
                  

                  

                    126
                    2x
                    
                      
        }else if (nrow(mydf) < 1){

                    		
                  

                  

                    127
                    1x
                    
                      
            fail("No record where TS.TSPARMCD=AEDICT.")

                    		
                  

                  

                    128
                    1x
                    
                      
        }else if (nrow(mydf) > 1){

                    		
                  

                  

                    129
                    1x
                    
                      
            fail("Multiple records where TS.TSPARMCD=AEDICT.",mydf)

                    		
                  

                  

                    130
                    
                    
                      
        }

                    		
                  

                  

                    131
                    
                    
                      
    }

                    		
                  

                  

                    132
                    
                    
                      
}

roche_derive_rave_row <- function(dts,domains=c("ae","cm","ds","lb","pr","ss","tr","tu")) {

                    		
                  

                  

                    38
                    
                    
                      
  

                    		
                  

                  

                    39
                    19x
                    
                      
  myvec <- paste0(toupper(unlist(domains)), "SPID")

                    		
                  

                  

                    40
                    
                    
                      
  

                    		
                  

                  

                    41
                    19x
                    
                      
  thevar=intersect(names(dts), myvec) #get --SPID variable of interest

                    		
                  

                  

                    42
                    
                    
                      
  

                    		
                  

                  

                    43
                    19x
                    
                      
  if(length(thevar)==1) { #Only create RAVE column if there is a --SPID variable

                    		
                  

                  

                    44
                    
                    
                      
    

                    		
                  

                  

                    45
                    
                    
                      
    # Extract RAVE row number, finding the last occurrence of -R:

                    		
                  

                  

                    46
                    17x
                    
                      
    RAVE_ROW <- ifelse(grepl("-R:", dts[[thevar]]),

                    		
                  

                  

                    47
                    17x
                    
                      
                       sub("/.*-R:", "#", dts[[thevar]]),

                    		
                  

                  

                    48
                    
                    
                      
                       "")

                    		
                  

                  

                    49
                    17x
                    
                      
    RAVE_ROW <- sub("/.*", "", RAVE_ROW)

                    		
                  

                  

                    50
                    
                    
                      
    

                    		
                  

                  

                    51
                    
                    
                      
    # Extract RAVE form name

                    		
                  

                  

                    52
                    17x
                    
                      
    RAVE_FORM <- ifelse(startsWith(as.character(dts[[thevar]]), "/F:")

                    		
                  

                  

                    53
                    17x
                    
                      
                        & grepl("-D:", dts[[thevar]]),

                    		
                  

                  

                    54
                    17x
                    
                      
                        sub("-D:.*", "", substring(dts[[thevar]], 4)),

                    		
                  

                  

                    55
                    
                    
                      
                        "")

                    		
                  

                  

                    56
                    
                    
                      
    

                    		
                  

                  

                    57
                    17x
                    
                      
    dts[["RAVE"]] <- paste0(RAVE_FORM, RAVE_ROW)

                    		
                  

                  

                    58
                    17x
                    
                      
    attr(dts[["RAVE"]], "label") <- "Rave Form"

                    		
                  

                  

                    59
                    
                    
                      
    

                    		
                  

                  

                    60
                    17x
                    
                      
    return(dts)

                    		
                  

                  

                    61
                    
                    
                      
    

                    		
                  

                  

                    62
                    
                    
                      
  }else(

                    		
                  

                  

                    63
                    2x
                    
                      
    return(dts)

                    		
                  

                  

                    64
                    
                    
                      
  )

                    		
                  

                  

                    65
                    
                    
                      
}

roche_covid_df <- function(TS=NULL){

                    		
                  

                  

                    108
                    
                    
                      
  

                    		
                  

                  

                    109
                    
                    
                      
  # Check if there is ts domain in data pack

                    		
                  

                  

                    110
                    !
                    
                      
  if (!is.null(TS)) {

                    		
                  

                  

                    111
                    
                    
                      
    

                    		
                  

                  

                    112
                    
                    
                      
    # Keep only TSVAL and TSVALn for TSPARAMCD = "AEDICT"

                    		
                  

                  

                    113
                    !
                    
                      
    tsval <- subset(TS, TS$TSPARMCD=="AEDICT", "TSVAL")

                    		
                  

                  

                    114
                    
                    
                      
    

                    		
                  

                  

                    115
                    
                    
                      
    # Check if there is TSPARAMCD = "AEDICT" in ts domain

                    		
                  

                  

                    116
                    !
                    
                      
    if (nrow(tsval) > 0) {

                    		
                  

                  

                    117
                    !
                    
                      
      versions <- as.vector(tsval[[1]])

                    		
                  

                  

                    118
                    
                    
                      
      

                    		
                  

                  

                    119
                    !
                    
                      
      condition <- ifelse(length(versions) == 1, TRUE, all(versions[1] == versions))

                    		
                  

                  

                    120
                    
                    
                      
      # Check if there are more than one record with TSPARAMCD = "AEDICT" and if there are equal versions of MedDRA in TSVAL values

                    		
                  

                  

                    121
                    !
                    
                      
      if (condition) {

                    		
                  

                  

                    122
                    
                    
                      
        # Check if all TSVAL values are missing

                    		
                  

                  

                    123
                    !
                    
                      
        if (is_sas_na(versions[1])) {

                    		
                  

                  

                    124
                    !
                    
                      
          covid_df_name <- 'covid'

                    		
                  

                  

                    125
                    
                    
                      
        } else {

                    		
                  

                  

                    126
                    !
                    
                      
          version <- versions[1]

                    		
                  

                  

                    127
                    !
                    
                      
          v_n <- as.numeric(unlist(regmatches(version, gregexpr("[0-9]+", version))))

                    		
                  

                  

                    128
                    !
                    
                      
          version_n <- as.numeric(paste0(v_n[1], v_n[2]))

                    		
                  

                  

                    129
                    
                    
                      
          

                    		
                  

                  

                    130
                    
                    
                      
          # Available MedDRA versions with COVID baskets

                    		
                  

                  

                    131
                    !
                    
                      
          covid_dt <- list.files(path = "data/", pattern = "covid")

                    		
                  

                  

                    132
                    !
                    
                      
          covid_n <- as.numeric(unlist(regmatches(covid_dt, gregexpr("[0-9]+", covid_dt))))

                    		
                  

                  

                    133
                    
                    
                      
          

                    		
                  

                  

                    134
                    
                    
                      
          # Check if MedDRA version is one of available list

                    		
                  

                  

                    135
                    !
                    
                      
          if (version_n %in% covid_n) {

                    		
                  

                  

                    136
                    !
                    
                      
            covid_df_name <- paste0('covid',version_n)

                    		
                  

                  

                    137
                    
                    
                      
          } else {

                    		
                  

                  

                    138
                    !
                    
                      
            covid_df_name <- 'covid'

                    		
                  

                  

                    139
                    
                    
                      
          }

                    		
                  

                  

                    140
                    
                    
                      
        }

                    		
                  

                  

                    141
                    
                    
                      
      }

                    		
                  

                  

                    142
                    
                    
                      
    } else {

                    		
                  

                  

                    143
                    !
                    
                      
      covid_df_name <- 'covid'

                    		
                  

                  

                    144
                    
                    
                      
    }

                    		
                  

                  

                    145
                    
                    
                      
  } else {

                    		
                  

                  

                    146
                    !
                    
                      
    covid_df_name <- 'covid'

                    		
                  

                  

                    147
                    
                    
                      
  }

                    		
                  

                  

                    148
                    
                    
                      
  

                    		
                  

                  

                    149
                    !
                    
                      
    return(get(covid_df_name))

                    		
                  

                  

                    150
                    
                    
                      
}

check_ex_exdose_pos_exoccur_no <- function(EX, drug=NULL) {

                    		
                  

                  

                    44
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    45
                    
                    
                      
    # Checks if required variables are present

                    		
                  

                  

                    46
                    9x
                    
                      
    if (EX %lacks_any% c("USUBJID","EXTRT","EXSTDTC","EXOCCUR","EXDOSE", "VISIT")) {

                    		
                  

                  

                    47
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    48
                    !
                    
                      
        fail(lacks_msg(EX, c("USUBJID","EXTRT","EXSTDTC","EXOCCUR","EXDOSE","VISIT")))

                    		
                  

                  

                    49
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    50
                    
                    
                      
        # Checks validity of drug name argument

                    		
                  

                  

                    51
                    8x
                    
                      
    } else if (!is.null(drug) && !(drug %in% EX[["EXTRT"]])) {

                    		
                  

                  

                    52
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    53
                    !
                    
                      
        fail(msg = "Drug name not found in dataset. ")

                    		
                  

                  

                    54
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    55
                    
                    
                      
    } else {

                    		
                  

                  

                    56
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    57
                    
                    
                      
        # Subsets EX to rows where EXOCCUR is not "Y" but EXDOSE is positive

                    		
                  

                  

                    58
                    8x
                    
                      
        df <- EX %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    59
                    8x
                    
                      
            select("USUBJID", "EXTRT", "EXSTDTC", "EXOCCUR", "EXDOSE", "VISIT") %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    60
                    8x
                    
                      
            filter(EX$EXOCCUR != "Y" & EX$EXDOSE > 0)

                    		
                  

                  

                    61
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    62
                    8x
                    
                      
        if (!is.null(drug)) {

                    		
                  

                  

                    63
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    64
                    !
                    
                      
            df <- df %>% filter(df$EXTRT == drug)

                    		
                  

                  

                    65
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    66
                    
                    
                      
        }

                    		
                  

                  

                    67
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    68
                    
                    
                      
        # Returns message depending on if there are records with positive dose

                    		
                  

                  

                    69
                    
                    
                      
        # but occurrence not marked as "Y"

                    		
                  

                  

                    70
                    8x
                    
                      
        if (nrow(df) != 0 && !is.null(drug)) {

                    		
                  

                  

                    71
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    72
                    !
                    
                      
            fail(paste0("There are ", length(unique(df$USUBJID)), " patients with ",

                    		
                  

                  

                    73
                    !
                    
                      
                        "positive dose amount (EXDOSE>0) when occurrence (EXOCCUR) for ",

                    		
                  

                  

                    74
                    !
                    
                      
                        drug, " is not 'Y'. "), df)

                    		
                  

                  

                    75
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    76
                    8x
                    
                      
        } else if (nrow(df) != 0) {

                    		
                  

                  

                    77
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    78
                    4x
                    
                      
            fail(paste0("There are ", length(unique(df$USUBJID)), " patients with ",

                    		
                  

                  

                    79
                    4x
                    
                      
                        "positive dose amount (EXDOSE>0) when occurrence (EXOCCUR)",

                    		
                  

                  

                    80
                    4x
                    
                      
                        " is not 'Y'. "), df)

                    		
                  

                  

                    81
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    82

            pass()

                    11x

                    67
                    10x

                    68
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    69
                    !
