check_ex_exdosu <- function(EX){

                    		
                  

                  

                    40
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    41
                    
                    
                      
  ###First bifurcate EX into a df based on occurrence of EXOCCUR

                    		
                  

                  

                    42
                    4x
                    
                      
  if ("EXOCCUR" %in% names(EX)) {

                    		
                  

                  

                    43
                    3x
                    
                      
    df <- EX %>% filter(EXOCCUR == "Y")

                    		
                  

                  

                    44
                    
                    
                      
  }

                    		
                  

                  

                    45
                    
                    
                      
  else {

                    		
                  

                  

                    46
                    1x
                    
                      
    df <- EX

                    		
                  

                  

                    47
                    
                    
                      
  }

                    		
                  

                  

                    48
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    49
                    
                    
                      
  ###Check that required variables exist and return a message if they don't

                    		
                  

                  

                    50
                    4x
                    
                      
  if(EX %lacks_any% c("USUBJID","EXTRT","EXSTDTC","EXDOSE","EXDOSU"))

                    		
                  

                  

                    51
                    
                    
                      
  {

                    		
                  

                  

                    52
                    1x
                    
                      
    fail(lacks_msg(EX, c("USUBJID", "EXTRT", "EXSTDTC","EXDOSE","EXDOSU")))

                    		
                  

                  

                    53
                    
                    
                      
  }

                    		
                  

                  

                    54
                    
                    
                      
  else

                    		
                  

                  

                    55
                    
                    
                      
  {

                    		
                  

                  

                    56
                    
                    
                      
    ### Subset EX to only records with missing EXDOSU

                    		
                  

                  

                    57
                    3x
                    
                      
    df <- df %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    58
                    
                    
                      
      # select all variables matching regular expressions.

                    		
                  

                  

                    59
                    3x
                    
                      
      select(matches(match = "USUBJID$|EXTRT$|EXSTDTC$|EXSTDTC$|EXDOSE$|EXDOSU$")) %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    60
                    
                    
                      
      # order

                    		
                  

                  

                    61
                    3x
                    
                      
      select(USUBJID, EXTRT, EXDOSE, EXSTDTC, EXDOSE, EXDOSU) %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    62
                    
                    
                      
      # filter missing EXDOSU obs

                    		
                  

                  

                    63
                    3x
                    
                      
      filter(is_sas_na(EXDOSU))

                    		
                  

                  

                    64

                    3x

                    67

                    68
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    69
                    
                    
                      
    ### Return message if no records in df

                    		
                  

                  

                    70
                    3x
                    
                      
    if(nrow(df)==0)

                    		
                  

                  

                    71
                    
                    
                      
    {

                    		
                  

                  

                    72
                    2x
                    
                      
      pass()

                    		
                  

                  

                    73
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    74
                    
                    
                      
      ### Return subset dataframe if there are records with missing EXDOSU

                    		
                  

                  

                    75
                    
                    
                      
    }

                    		
                  

                  

                    76
                    1x
                    
                      
    else if(nrow(df)>0)

                    		
                  

                  

                    77
                    
                    
                      
    {

                    		
                  

                  

                    78
                    1x
                    
                      
      fail(

                    		
                  

                  

                    79
                    1x
                    
                      
        msg = paste0("There are ",nrow(df)," records with missing dose units. "), data = df)

  }

check_vs_height <- function(VS,DM){

                    		
                  

                  

                    45
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    46
                    5x
                    
                      
  if(VS %lacks_any% c("USUBJID", "VSTEST", "VSSTRESN")){

                    		
                  

                  

                    47
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    48
                    1x
                    
                      
    fail(lacks_msg(VS, c("USUBJID", "VSTEST", "VSSTRESN")))

                    		
                  

                  

                    49
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    50
                    4x
                    
                      
  }else if(DM %lacks_any% c("USUBJID")){

                    		
                  

                  

                    51
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    52
                    1x
                    
                      
    fail(lacks_msg(DM,c("USUBJID")))

                    		
                  

                  

                    53
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    54
                    
                    
                      
  }else{

                    		
                  

                  

                    55
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    56
                    
                    
                      
    ### Obtain dataset containing all patients in VS with a valid height

                    		
                  

                  

                    57
                    3x
                    
                      
    vs_pats <- VS %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    58
                    3x
                    
                      
      filter(toupper(VSTEST) == "HEIGHT") %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    59
                    3x
                    
                      
      filter(!is_sas_na(VSSTRESN)) %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    60
                    3x
                    
                      
      select(USUBJID)

                    		
                  

                  

                    61
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    62
                    
                    
                      
    ### Obtain list of patients in DM

                    		
                  

                  

                    63
                    3x
                    
                      
    dm_pats <- DM %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    64
                    3x
                    
                      
      select(USUBJID)

                    		
                  

                  

                    65
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    66
                    
                    
                      
    ### Obtain patients in dm_pats who don't appear in vs_pats

                    		
                  

                  

                    67
                    3x
                    
                      
    mydf <- dm_pats %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    68
                    3x
                    
                      
      anti_join(vs_pats, by = "USUBJID")

                    		
                  

                  

                    69
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    70
                    
                    
                      
    ### Print to report

                    		
                  

                  

                    71
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    72
                    
                    
                      
    ### Return message if no records with missing HEIGHT

                    		
                  

                  

                    73
                    3x
                    
                      
    if(nrow(mydf)==0){

                    		
                  

                  

                    74
                    1x
                    
                      
      pass()

                    		
                  

                  

                    75
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    76
                    
                    
                      
      ### Return subset dataframe if there are records with missing HEIGHT

                    		
                  

                  

                    77
                    
                    
                      
    }else{

                    		
                  

                  

                    78
                    2x
                    
                      
      fail(

                    		
                  

                  

                    79
                    2x
                    
                      
        paste0("There are ",nrow(mydf)," patients with no recorded height at any visit. "),

                    		
                  

                  

                    80
                    2x
                    
                      
        mydf)

                    		
                  

                  

                    81
                    
                    
                      
    }

  }

                    		
                  

                  

                    83
                    
                    
                      
}

                    87
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    88
                    
                    
                      
    ###First check that required variables exist and return a message if they don't

                    8x

                    90
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    91
                    1x

                    7x
                    
                      
    }else if( TS %lacks_any% c("TSPARMCD", "TSPARM", "TSVAL")){

                    6x
                    
                      
    }else if (!("SSTDTC" %in% TS[["TSPARMCD"]])) {

                    		
                  

                  

                    98
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    99
                    1x
                    
                      
        fail("TS.TSPARMCD = 'SSTDTC' (Study Start Date), which is required for FDA submissions, not found. Date in TSVAL should correspond with earliest informed consent date of enrolled patient. ")

                    		
                  

                  

                    100
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    101

                    102
                    
                    
                      
    else{

                    		
                  

                  

                    103
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    104
                    
                    
                      
        ### Subset TS to only SSTDTC record

                    		
                  

                  

                    105
                    5x
                    
                      
        mydf <- subset(TS, TS$TSPARMCD=="SSTDTC", c("TSPARMCD", "TSPARM","TSVAL"))

                    		
                  

                  

                    106
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    107
                    5x
                    
                      
        mydf$DS_FIRST_ICDATE <- NA

                    110
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    111
                    5x

                    136
                    1x

                    150
                    !

                    151

                    153
                    2x

                    154
                    1x
                    
                      
                pass()

check_ae_aeout <- function(AE,preproc=identity,...){

                    		
                  

                  

                    42
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    43
                    9x
                    
                      
    if (AE %lacks_any% c("USUBJID", "AEDTHDTC", "AEOUT")) {

                    		
                  

                  

                    44
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    45
                    !
                    
                      
        fail(lacks_msg(AE, c("USUBJID", "AEDTHDTC", "AEOUT" )))

                    		
                  

                  

                    46
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    47
                    
                    
                      
    } else {

                    		
                  

                  

                    48
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    49
                    
                    
                      
        #Apply company specific preprocessing function

                    		
                  

                  

                    50
                    8x
                    
                      
        AE = preproc(AE,...)

                    		
                  

                  

                    51
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    52
                    8x
                    
                      
        df <- AE %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    53
                    8x
                    
                      
            filter((!is_sas_na(AEDTHDTC) & AEOUT != "FATAL") | (AEOUT=="FATAL" & is_sas_na(AEDTHDTC))) %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    54
                    8x

                    56
                    8x

                    57
                    4x

                    58
                    
                    
                      
        } else {

                    		
                  

                  

                    59
                    4x
                    
                      
            pass()

                    		
                  

                  

                    60
                    
                    
                      
        }

                    		
                  

                  

                    61
                    
                    
                      
    }

                    		
                  

                  

                    62
                    
                    
                      
}

#' @title Run all checks in sdtmchecks package using parallel processing

                    		
                  

                  

                    2
                    
                    
                      
#'

                    		
                  

                  

                    3
                    
                    
                      
#' @description This function runs all checks in the sdtmchecks package.  It expects sdtm domains saved as dataframe objects in your global environment.  These dataframes should have lowercase names, e.g. dm.

                    		
                  

                  

                    4
                    
                    
                      
#'

                    		
                  

                  

                    5
                    
                    
                      
#' @param type  Type of data checks, i.e. c("ALL", "ONC", "COV", "PRO", "OPHTH"). NULL runs all type.

                    		
                  

                  

                    6
                    
                    
                      
#'

                    		
                  

                  

                    7
                    
                    
                      
#' @param priority Type of data checks priority, i.e. c("High", "Medium", "Low"). NULL runs all priority.

                    		
                  

                  

                    8
                    
                    
                      
#'

                    		
                  

                  

                    9
                    
                    
                      
#' @param verbose Whether to display messages while running

                    		
                  

                  

                    10
                    
                    
                      
#'

                    		
                  

                  

                    11
                    
                    
                      
#' @param metads Metadata to use to execute the checks.  The default is the sdtmchecksmeta dataframe available in the packages.  This object could easily be customized, e.g subset, etc.

                    		
                  

                  

                    12
                    
                    
                      
#'

                    		
                  

                  

                    13
                    
                    
                      
#' @param ncores Number of cores for parallel processing, default is 1 (sequential)

                    		
                  

                  

                    14
                    
                    
                      
#'

                    		
                  

                  

                    15
                    
                    
                      
#' @details to look up documentation for the data checks package, please use command ??sdtmchecks

                    		
                  

                  

                    16
                    
                    
                      
#'

                    		
                  

                  

                    17
                    
                    
                      
#' @return list with results from individual checks

                    		
                  

                  

                    18
                    
                    
                      
#'

                    		
                  

                  

                    19
                    
                    
                      
#' @importFrom parallel mcmapply

                    		
                  

                  

                    20
                    
                    
                      
#' 

                    		
                  

                  

                    21
                    
                    
                      
#' @family ex_rpt

                    		
                  

                  

                    22
                    
                    
                      
#' 

                    		
                  

                  

                    23
                    
                    
                      
#' @keywords ex_rpt

                    		
                  

                  

                    24
                    
                    
                      
#'

                    		
                  

                  

                    25
                    
                    
                      
#' @export

                    		
                  

                  

                    26
                    
                    
                      
#'

                    		
                  

                  

                    27
                    
                    
                      
#' @examples

                    		
                  

                  

                    28
                    
                    
                      
#'

                    		
                  

                  

                    29
                    
                    
                      
#' \dontrun{

                    		
                  

                  

                    30
                    
                    
                      
#' 

                    		
                  

                  

                    31
                    
                    
                      
#' # Assuming sdtm datasets are in your global environment

                    		
                  

                  

                    32
                    
                    
                      
#' all_rec<-run_all_checks(metads=sdtmchecksmeta, 

                    		
                  

                  

                    33
                    
                    
                      
#'                         priority=c("High","Medium","Low"), 

                    		
                  

                  

                    34
                    
                    
                      
#'                         type=c("ALL", "ONC", "COVID", "PRO"))

                    		
                  

                  

                    35
                    
                    
                      
#' all_rec<-run_all_checks(metads=sdtmchecksmeta, 

                    		
                  

                  

                    36
                    
                    
                      
#'                         priority=NULL, 

                    		
                  

                  

                    37
                    
                    
                      
#'                         type=c("ONC", "COVID", "PRO"))

                    		
                  

                  

                    38
                    
                    
                      
#' }

                    		
                  

                  

                    39
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    40
                    
                    
                      
run_all_checks <- function(metads = sdtmchecksmeta,

                    		
                  

                  

                    41
                    
                    
                      
                           priority = c("High", "Medium", "Low"),

                    		
                  

                  

                    42
                    
                    
                      
                           type = c("ALL", "ONC", "COVID", "PRO", "OPHTH"),

                    		
                  

                  

                    43
                    
                    
                      
                           verbose = TRUE,

                    		
                  

                  

                    44
                    
                    
                      
                           ncores = 1) {

                    		
                  

                  

                    45
                    
                    
                      
    

                    		
                  

                  

                    46
                    !
                    
                      
    if (!is.null(priority) & !all(priority %in% c("High", "Medium", "Low"))) {

                    		
                  

                  

                    47
                    !
                    
                      
        stop("priority argument should only take values 'High','Medium', or 'Low'")

                    		
                  

                  

                    48
                    
                    
                      
    }

                    		
                  

                  

                    49
                    !
                    
                      
    if (!is.null(type) & !all(type %in% c("ALL", "ONC", "COVID", "PRO","OPHTH"))) {

                    		
                  

                  

                    50
                    !
                    
                      
        stop("type argument should only take values 'ALL', 'ONC', 'COVID', 'PRO', 'OPHTH'")

                    		
                  

                  

                    51
                    
                    
                      
    }

                    		
                  

                  

                    52
                    
                    
                      
    

                    		
                  

                  

                    53
                    
                    
                      
    # subset meta dataset for specific Type and Priority

                    		
                  

                  

                    54
                    !
                    
                      
    if(!is.null(priority)){

                    		
                  

                  

                    55
                    !
                    
                      
        metads <-subset(metads,metads$priority %in% priority)

                    		
                  

                  

                    56
                    
                    
                      
    }

                    		
                  

                  

                    57
                    !
                    
                      
    if(!is.null(type)){

                    		
                  

                  

                    58
                    !
                    
                      
        metads <-subset(metads,metads$category %in% type)

                    		
                  

                  

                    59
                    
                    
                      
    }

                    		
                  

                  

                    60
                    
                    
                      
    

                    		
                  

                  

                    61
                    
                    
                      
    #Identify missing expected domains to cat out to the user later

                    		
                  

                  

                    62
                    !
                    
                      
    expected.domains = sort(unique(strsplit(gsub(" ","",paste(unique(metads$domains),collapse=",")),",")[[1]]))

                    		
                  

                  

                    63
                    !
                    
                      
    missing.domains = expected.domains[!(expected.domains %in% ls(envir = .GlobalEnv))]

                    		
                  

                  

                    64
                    
                    
                      
    

                    		
                  

                  

                    65
                    
                    
                      
    # Run checks

                    		
                  

                  

                    66
                    
                    
                      
    

                    		
                  

                  

                    67
                    !
                    
                      
    all_rec <- mcmapply(

                    		
                  

                  

                    68
                    !
                    
                      
        FUN = run_check,

                    		
                  

                  

                    69
                    !
                    
                      
        metads$check, metads$fxn_in, metads$xls_title, metads$pdf_title, metads$pdf_subtitle, metads$pdf_return, verbose,

                    		
                  

                  

                    70
                    !
                    
                      
        SIMPLIFY = FALSE,  # forces mcmapply to return a list

                    		
                  

                  

                    71
                    !
                    
                      
        USE.NAMES = TRUE,  # generates list names

                    		
                  

                  

                    72
                    !
                    
                      
        mc.cores = ncores

                    		
                  

                  

                    73
                    
                    
                      
    )

                    		
                  

                  

                    74
                    
                    
                      
    

                    		
                  

                  

                    75
                    !
                    
                      
    if (verbose == TRUE & length(missing.domains) > 0) {

                    		
                  

                  

                    76
                    !
                    
                      
        cat(

                    		
                  

                  

                    77
                    !
                    
                      
            paste0(

                    		
                  

                  

                    78
                    !
                    
                      
                "\nDomain not found: ",

                    		
                  

                  

                    79
                    !
                    
                      
                missing.domains,

                    		
                  

                  

                    80
                    !
                    
                      
                ". Checks requiring this domain were not run."

                    		
                  

                  

                    81
                    
                    
                      
            )

                    		
                  

                  

                    82
                    
                    
                      
        )

                    		
                  

                  

                    83
                    
                    
                      
    }

                    		
                  

                  

                    84
                    
                    
                      
    

                    		
                  

                  

                    85
                    !
                    
                      
    cat("\n")

                    		
                  

                  

                    86
                    
                    
                      
    

                    		
                  

                  

                    87
                    
                    
                      
    # return the final list

                    		
                  

                  

                    88
                    !
                    
                      
    return(all_rec)

                    		
                  

                  

                    89
                    
                    
                      
    

                    		
                  

                  

                    90
                    
                    
                      
} # end of function

check_ae_dup <- function(AE){

                    		
                  

                  

                    32
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    33
                    
                    
                      
    # Checks whether required variables are in dataset

                    		
                  

                  

                    34
                    3x
                    
                      
    if (AE %lacks_any% c("USUBJID", "AEDECOD", "AESTDTC", "AEENDTC", "AETERM")) {

                    		
                  

                  

                    35
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    36
                    !

                    37
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    38
                    3x
                    
                      
    } else if (AE %has_all% c("AETOXGR", "AESEV")) {

                    		
                  

                  

                    39
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    40
                    !
                    
                      
        fail("AE has both variables: AETOXGR and AESEV.")

                    		
                  

                  

                    41

                    3x

                    !

    } else {

                    		
                  

                  

                    47

        # Use either AETOXGR or AESEV, depending on which is in the AE dataset

                    		
                  

                  

                    49
                    3x
                    
                      
        toxgr_var <- if(AE %has_all% "AETOXGR") "AETOXGR" else "AESEV"

                    3x
                    
                      
        lat_var <- if (AE %has_all% "AELAT") "AELAT" else NULL

                    		
                  

                  

                    51
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    52
                    3x

                    53

                    54

            df <- AE %>%

                    3x

            # When AEMODIFY in AE

                    63
                    !

                    66

                    67
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    68

                    69
                    3x
                    
                      
        if (nrow(df) != 0) {

                    		
                  

                  

                    70

check_ds_dsdecod_death <- function(DS,preproc=identity,...){

                    		
                  

                  

                    49
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    50
                    !
                    
                      
    if (DS %lacks_any% c("USUBJID", "DSDECOD", "DSSCAT")) {

                    		
                  

                  

                    51
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    52
                    !
                    
                      
        fail(lacks_msg(DS, c("USUBJID", "DSDECOD", "DSSCAT")))

                    		
                  

                  

                    53
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    54
                    
                    
                      
    } else {

                    		
                  

                  

                    55
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    56
                    
                    
                      
        #Apply company specific preprocessing function

                    		
                  

                  

                    57

                    58

        DS <- DS %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    59

                    60
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    61
                    
                    
                      
        # Subset DS death records and include only records without a STUDY

                    		
                  

                  

                    62
                    
                    
                      
        # COMPLETION/DISCONTINUATION form

                    		
                  

                  

                    63
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    64
                    
                    
                      
        # find records with DEATH indicated in DS - note that these are not

                    		
                  

                  

                    65
                    
                    
                      
        # necessarily unique by USUBJID

                    		
                  

                  

                    66
                    !
                    
                      
        ref <- DS %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    67
                    !
                    
                      
            filter(grepl("DEATH", toupper(DSDECOD)))

                    		
                  

                  

                    68
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    69
                    
                    
                      
        # find patients that have a STUDY DISCONTINUATION record

                    		
                  

                  

                    70
                    !
                    
                      
        discon <- DS %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    71
                    !
                    
                      
            filter(

                    		
                  

                  

                    72
                    !
                    
                      
                grepl("STUDY", toupper(DSSCAT)),

                    		
                  

                  

                    73
                    !
                    
                      
                grepl("DISCON", toupper(DSSCAT)),

                    		
                  

                  

                    74
                    !
                    
                      
                !grepl("DRUG", toupper(DSSCAT)),

                    		
                  

                  

                    75
                    !
                    
                      
                !grepl("TREATMENT", toupper(DSSCAT))

                    		
                  

                  

                    76
                    
                    
                      
            ) %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    77
                    !
                    
                      
            mutate(DISCFL="Y") %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    78
                    !
                    
                      
            select(USUBJID, DISCFL)

                    		
                  

                  

                    79
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    80
                    !
                    
                      
        discon <- distinct(discon)

                    		
                  

                  

                    81
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    82
                    
                    
                      
        # merge datasets to output only patients without DISCON records in DS

                    		
                  

                  

                    83
                    
                    
                      
        # but known to have died

                    		
                  

                  

                    84
                    !
                    
                      
        mydf0 <- merge(

                    		
                  

                  

                    85
                    !
                    
                      
                x = ref,

                    		
                  

                  

                    86
                    !
                    
                      
                y = discon,

                    		
                  

                  

                    87
                    !
                    
                      
                by = c("USUBJID"),

                    		
                  

                  

                    88
                    !
                    
                      
                all.x = TRUE,

                    		
                  

                  

                    89
                    !
                    
                      
                all.y = FALSE

                    		
                  

                  

                    90
                    
                    
                      
            )

                    		
                  

                  

                    91
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    92
                    !
                    
                      
        mydf <- mydf0 %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    93
                    !
                    
                      
            filter(is_sas_na(DISCFL)) %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    94
                    !
                    
                      
            select(-any_of(c("DISCFL", "DSSCAT")))

                    		
                  

                  

                    95
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    96
                    
                    
                      
        # replace <NA> with blank in DSSCAT

                    		
                  

                  

                    97
                    !
                    
                      
        mydf[is.na(mydf)] <- ""

                    		
                  

                  

                    98
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    99
                    !
                    
                      
        rownames(mydf)=NULL

                    		
                  

                  

                    100
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    101
                    !
                    
                      
        if (nrow(mydf) == 0) {

                    		
                  

                  

                    102
                    !
                    
                      
            pass()

                    		
                  

                  

                    103
                    
                    
                      
        } else {

                    		
                  

                  

                    104
                    !
                    
                      
            fail(

                    		
                  

                  

                    105
                    !
                    
                      
                paste(nrow(mydf), "record(s) for",

                    		
                  

                  

                    106
                    !
                    
                      
                      length(unique(mydf$USUBJID)),

                    		
                  

                  

                    107
                    !
                    
                      
                      "unique patient(s) with DSDECOD='DEATH' but no",

                    		
                  

                  

                    108
                    !
                    
                      
                    "record with DSSCAT indicating STUDY DISCONTINUATION. "

                    		
                  

                  

                    109
                    
                    
                      
                ),

                    		
                  

                  

                    110
                    !
                    
                      
                data = mydf

                    		
                  

                  

                    111
                    
                    
                      
            )

                    5x

                    5x

                    2x
                    
                      
        mypairs = unique(tusub)

                    		
                  

                  

                    49
                    2x
                    
                      
        mypairs$x = 1

                    		
                  

                  

                    50
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    51
                    
                    
                      
        ### Get counts of visit values per date for each subject

                    		
                  

                  

                    52
                    2x
                    
                      
        mydf0 = aggregate(mypairs$x,by=list(USUBJID=mypairs$USUBJID, TUDTC=mypairs$TUDTC),FUN=sum)

                    		
                  

                  

                    53
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    54
                    
                    
                      
        ### Subset where count is >1 and output

                    		
                  

                  

                    55
                    2x
                    
                      
        mydf0 = mydf0 %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    56
                    2x
                    
                      
            select(USUBJID, TUDTC) %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    57
                    2x
                    
                      
            filter(mydf0$x>1)

                    		
                  

                  

                    58
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    59
                    2x
                    
                      
        mypairs0 = mypairs %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    60
                    2x
                    
                      
            select(USUBJID, TUDTC,VISIT)

                    		
                  

                  

                    61
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    62
                    2x
                    
                      
        mydf = merge(mydf0,mypairs0,by=c('USUBJID','TUDTC'),all.x = TRUE)

                    		
                  

                  

                    63
                    2x
                    
                      
        rownames(mydf)=NULL

                    		
                  

                  

                    64
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    65
                    
                    
                      
        ### if no consistency

                    		
                  

                  

                    66
                    2x
                    
                      
        if (nrow(mydf)==0) {

                    		
                  

                  

                    67
                    1x
                    
                      
            pass()

                    		
                  

                  

                    68
                    1x
                    
                      
        } else if (nrow(mydf) > 0) {

                    		
                  

                  

                    69
                    
                    
                      
            ### Return subset dataframe if there are records with inconsistency

                    		
                  

                  

                    70
                    1x
                    
                      
            fail(paste("There are",nrow(mydf),"TU records where the same date occurs accross multiple visits. "),

                    		
                  

                  

                    71
                    1x
                    
                      
                 mydf)

                    		
                  

                  

                    72
                    
                    
                      
        }

                    		
                  

                  

                    73
                    
                    
                      
    }

                    		
                  

                  

                    74
                    
                    
                      
}

#' @title Check for conmed dates with year and day known but month unknown

                    		
                  

                  

                    2
                    
                    
                      
#'

                    		
                  

                  

                    3
                    
                    
                      
#' @description Check for missing month when conmed start (CMSTDTC) or end dates

                    		
                  

                  

                    4

                    5

                    6
                    
                    
                      
#' @param CM Concomitant Medications SDTM dataset with variables USUBJID, CMTRT,

                    		
                  

                  

                    7
                    
                    
                      
#' CMSTDTC, CMENDTC

                    		
                  

                  

                    8
                    
                    
                      
#' @param preproc An optional company specific preprocessing script

                    		
                  

                  

                    9
                    
                    
                      
#' @param ... Other arguments passed to methods

                    		
                  

                  

                    10
                    
                    
                      
#'

                    		
                  

                  

                    11
                    
                    
                      
#' @importFrom dplyr %>% select

                    17
                    
                    
                      
#' @export

                    		
                  

                  

                    18

check_cm_missing_month <- function(CM,preproc=identity,...){

                    		
                  

                  

                    42
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    43
                    
                    
                      
###First check that required variables exist and return a message if they don't

                    		
                  

                  

                    44
                    3x
                    
                      
if(CM %lacks_any% c("USUBJID", "CMTRT", "CMSTDTC","CMENDTC")){

                    		
                  

                  

                    45
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    46
                    1x
                    
                      
    fail(lacks_msg(CM, c("USUBJID", "CMTRT", "CMSTDTC","CMENDTC")))

                    		
                  

                  

                    47
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    48
                    
                    
                      
    } else{

                    		
                  

                  

                    49
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    50
                    
                    
                      
      #Apply company specific preprocessing function

                    		
                  

                  

                    51
                    2x
                    
                      
      CM = preproc(CM,...)

                    		
                  

                  

                    52
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    53
                    
                    
                      
        # check if CMSTDTC CMENDTC has missing month and is in format 'yyyy---dd'

                    		
                  

                  

                    54
                    2x
                    
                      
        mydf <- subset(CM,

                    		
                  

                  

                    55
                    2x
                    
                      
                       (missing_month(CMSTDTC) | missing_month(CMENDTC) ),

                    		
                  

                  

                    56
                    
                    
                      
                       ) %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    57
                    2x
                    
                      
          select(any_of(c("USUBJID", "CMTRT", "CMSTDTC","CMENDTC","RAVE")))

                    		
                  

                  

                    58
                    2x
                    
                      
        rownames(mydf)=NULL

                    		
                  

                  

                    59
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    60
                    
                    
                      
      ###Print to report

                    		
                  

                  

                    61
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    62
                    
                    
                      
      ### Return message if there are conmed start and end dates with only missing month

                    		
                  

                  

                    63
                    2x
                    
                      
      if(nrow(mydf)==0){

                    		
                  

                  

                    64
                    1x
                    
                      
        pass()

                    		
                  

                  

                    65
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    66
                    
                    
                      
        ### Return subset dataframe if there are records with inconsistency

                    		
                  

                  

                    67
                    1x
                    
                      
      }else if(nrow(mydf)>0){

                    		
                  

                  

                    68
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    69
                    1x
                    
                      
          fail(paste("There are ",length(unique(mydf$USUBJID)),

                    		
                  

                  

                    70
                    1x
                    
                      
                     " patients with a conmed date that has year and day present but missing month. ",sep=""),

                    		
                  

                  

                    71
                    1x
                    
                      
               mydf)

                    		
                  

                  

                    72
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    73
                    
                    
                      
        }

                    		
                  

                  

                    74
                    
                    
                      
      }

                    		
                  

                  

                    75
                    
                    
                      
}

#' @title Check if 1m BCVA test stops too late, too early and has correct total

                    		
                  

                  

                    2
                    
                    
                      
#'

                    		
                  

                  

                    3
                    
                    
                      
#' @description This ophthalmology check is for BCVA 1m test. It checks three conditions: <1> BCVA test stops too late,

                    		
                  

                  

                    4
                    
                    
                      
#' meaning that lines were read after number of correct letters is <= 3. <2> BCVA test stops too early, meaning that

                    		
                  

                  

                    5
                    
                    
                      
#' further lines were not read when all numbers of correct letters is > 3. <3> BCVA total score is not correct, meaning

                    		
                  

                  

                    6
                    
                    
                      
#' that the sum of the number of correct at 1 meter doesn't match with what has been recorded in eCRF

                    		
                  

                  

                    7
                    
                    
                      
#' (BCVA Scores eCRF Page - C. Total number correct at 1m).

                    		
                  

                  

                    8
                    
                    
                      
#' Please note that this check only works with USUBJID, VISIT, VISITNUM, OELOC, OELAT combination has unique

                    		
                  

                  

                    9
                    
                    
                      
#' dates (OEDTC). If your datasets are having situations like 1) unscheduled visits happening on different dates or

                    		
                  

                  

                    10
                    
                    
                      
#' 2) BCVA TOTAL happens on a different date from BCVA row tests, such combinations

                    		
                  

                  

                    11
                    
                    
                      
#' will be removed from check.

                    		
                  

                  

                    12
                    
                    
                      
#' Please note that this check excludes forms BCVA Low Vision Test (BCV5), BCVA Scores (BCV7),

                    		
                  

                  

                    13
                    
                    
                      
#' BCVA Low Luminance Scores (BCVLL5), BCVA Combined Assessments (BCVAC), BCVA Low Luminance Combined Assessments (BCVACLL)

                    		
                  

                  

                    14
                    
                    
                      
#' before running check as these forms do not include Row numbers.

                    		
                  

                  

                    15
                    
                    
                      
#'

                    		
                  

                  

                    16
                    
                    
                      
#' @param OE Ophtho Dataset with variables USUBJID, OESPID, OECAT, OESCAT, OETSTDTL, OESTRESN, OESTAT, OELOC, OELAT,

                    		
                  

                  

                    17
                    
                    
                      
#' OERESCAT, VISIT, VISITNUM, OEDTC, OEDY

                    		
                  

                  

                    18

                    19
                    
                    
                      
#' @return boolean value if check failed or passed with 'msg' attribute if the

                    21
