check_oe_bcva_1m_late_early_tot <- function(OE) {

                    		
                  

                  

                    104
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    105
                    5x
                    
                      
    required_variables <- c(

                    		
                  

                  

                    106
                    5x
                    
                      
        "USUBJID", "OECAT", "OESCAT", "OETSTDTL", "OESTAT", "OERESCAT", "VISIT", "VISITNUM", "OEDTC", "OEDY",

                    		
                  

                  

                    107
                    5x
                    
                      
        "OELOC", "OELAT", "OESTRESN"

                    		
                  

                  

                    108
                    
                    
                      
    )

                    		
                  

                  

                    109
                    5x
                    
                      
    output_variables <- c( "USUBJID", "OETSTDTL", "VISIT", "OEDTC", "OELAT", "OESTRESN")

                    		
                  

                  

                    110
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    111
                    5x
                    
                      
    str_match <- function(x, pattern) {

                    		
                  

                  

                    112
                    8x
                    
                      
        m <- regexpr(pattern, x)

                    		
                  

                  

                    113
                    8x
                    
                      
        regmatches(x, m)

                    		
                  

                  

                    114
                    
                    
                      
    }

                    		
                  

                  

                    115
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    116
                    5x
                    
                      
    to_upper_variables <- function(variables) {

                    		
                  

                  

                    117
                    40x
                    
                      
        if(is.character(variables)) return(toupper(variables))

                    		
                  

                  

                    118
                    12x
                    
                      
        else return(variables)

                    		
                  

                  

                    119
                    
                    
                      
    }

                    		
                  

                  

                    120
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    121
                    5x
                    
                      
    if(OE %lacks_any% c("OESPID")){

                    		
                  

                  

                    122
                    !
                    
                      
        fail(lacks_msg(OE, c("OESPID")))

                    		
                  

                  

                    123
                    5x
                    
                      
    } else if(OE %>% filter(!grepl("BCV5|BCV7|BCVLL5|BCVAC|BCVACLL", OESPID) &

                    		
                  

                  

                    124
                    5x
                    
                      
                            OECAT == "BEST CORRECTED VISUAL ACUITY" & OETSTDTL == "TESTING DISTANCE: 1M") %>% nrow() == 0){

                    		
                  

                  

                    125
                    !
                    
                      
        pass()

                    		
                  

                  

                    126
                    5x
                    
                      
    } else if (OE %lacks_any% required_variables) {

                    		
                  

                  

                    127
                    1x
                    
                      
        fail(lacks_msg(OE, required_variables))

                    		
                  

                  

                    128
                    
                    
                      
    } else {

                    		
                  

                  

                    129
                    
                    
                      
        # preprocessing OE dataset to get the relavant BCVA 1m test data

                    		
                  

                  

                    130
                    
                    
                      
        ### select required variables

                    		
                  

                  

                    131
                    4x
                    
                      
        BCVA_1m <- OE %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    132
                    4x
                    
                      
            select(all_of(required_variables))

                    		
                  

                  

                    133
                    
                    
                      
        ### change all character variables to uppercase for the OE subset dataset

                    		
                  

                  

                    134
                    
                    
                      
        # BCVA_1m <- data.frame(lapply(BCVA_1m, to_upper_variables))

                    		
                  

                  

                    135
                    4x
                    
                      
        for(var in required_variables){

                    		
                  

                  

                    136
                    52x
                    
                      
            BCVA_1m[[var]]=to_upper_variables(BCVA_1m[[var]])

                    		
                  

                  

                    137
                    
                    
                      
        }

                    		
                  

                  

                    138
                    
                    
                      
        ### filter on BCVA 1m criteria

                    		
                  

                  

                    139
                    4x
                    
                      
        BCVA_1m <- BCVA_1m %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    140
                    4x
                    
                      
            filter(OECAT == "BEST CORRECTED VISUAL ACUITY" & OETSTDTL == "TESTING DISTANCE: 1M" &

                    		
                  

                  

                    141
                    4x
                    
                      
                       (!OESTAT %in% c("NOT DONE", "ND")) & OESCAT != "LOW LUMINANCE")

                    		
                  

                  

                    142
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    143
                    
                    
                      
        # check if dates are unique for each USUBJID, VISITNUM, OELAT combination, if not, such a combination will be

                    		
                  

                  

                    144
                    
                    
                      
        # removed from the BCVA check including situations like 1) unscheduled visits on different dates, or 2) TOTAL

                    		
                  

                  

                    145
                    
                    
                      
        # date happens on a dfferent date from the BCVA test date

                    		
                  

                  

                    146
                    4x
                    
                      
        nonunique_dates_for_each_sub_visit <- BCVA_1m %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    147
                    4x
                    
                      
            group_by(USUBJID, VISIT, VISITNUM, OELAT) %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    148
                    4x
                    
                      
            summarise(num_of_dates = length(unique(OEDTC)), .groups = "drop") %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    149
                    4x
                    
                      
            filter(num_of_dates > 1) %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    150
                    4x
                    
                      
            ungroup()

                    		
                  

                  

                    151
                    4x
                    
                      
        BCVA_1m <- BCVA_1m %>% left_join(

                    		
                  

                  

                    152
                    4x
                    
                      
            nonunique_dates_for_each_sub_visit,

                    		
                  

                  

                    153
                    4x
                    
                      
            by = c("USUBJID", "VISIT", "VISITNUM", "OELAT")

                    		
                  

                  

                    154
                    
                    
                      
        ) %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    155
                    4x
                    
                      
            filter(is.na(num_of_dates)) %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    156
                    4x
                    
                      
            select( - num_of_dates)

                    		
                  

                  

                    157
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    158
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    159
                    
                    
                      
        # subcheck 1: if BCVA 1m test stops too late

                    		
                  

                  

                    160
                    4x
                    
                      
        anl1 <- BCVA_1m %>% filter(grepl("ROW \\d+ - SNELLEN \\d+/\\d+", OERESCAT)) %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    161
                    4x
                    
                      
            mutate(ROW = str_match(OERESCAT, "ROW \\d+"), ROWNUM = as.integer(str_match(ROW, "\\d+"))) %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    162
                    4x
                    
                      
            arrange(USUBJID, VISITNUM, OEDTC, OELAT, ROWNUM)

                    		
                  

                  

                    163
                    4x
                    
                      
        late_rows <- anl1 %>% group_by(USUBJID, VISITNUM, OEDTC, OELOC, OELAT) %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    164
                    4x
                    
                      
            mutate(LAG_OESTRESN = lag(OESTRESN)) %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    165
                    4x
                    
                      
            filter(LAG_OESTRESN <= 3) %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    166
                    4x
                    
                      
            mutate(MAX_ROW = ifelse(is.na(ROWNUM), NA, min(ROWNUM))) %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    167
                    4x
                    
                      
            filter(ROWNUM == MAX_ROW) %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    168
                    4x
                    
                      
            ungroup() %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    169
                    4x
                    
                      
            select(USUBJID, VISITNUM, OEDTC, OELOC, OELAT, MAX_ROW)

                    		
                  

                  

                    170
                    4x
                    
                      
        late1m <- anl1 %>% left_join(late_rows, by = c("USUBJID", "VISITNUM", "OEDTC", "OELOC", "OELAT")) %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    171
                    4x
                    
                      
            mutate(issue = ifelse(ROWNUM >= MAX_ROW, "BCVA 1m check stops too late", NA)) %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    172
                    4x
                    
                      
            filter(!is.na(issue) & OESTRESN != 0) %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    173
                    4x
                    
                      
            mutate(TOTAL = NA) %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    174
                    4x
                    
                      
            select(all_of(output_variables), TOTAL, issue) %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    175
                    4x
                    
                      
            unique()

                    		
                  

                  

                    176
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    177
                    
                    
                      
        # subcheck 2: if BCVA 1m test stops too early

                    		
                  

                  

                    178
                    
                    
                      
        ## anl2 is the same as anl1

                    		
                  

                  

                    179
                    4x
                    
                      
        early1m <- anl1 %>% group_by(USUBJID, VISITNUM, OEDTC, OELOC, OELAT) %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    180
                    4x
                    
                      
            mutate(LEAD_OESTRESN = lead(OESTRESN)) %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    181
                    4x
                    
                      
            filter(is.na(LEAD_OESTRESN) & OESTRESN > 3 & ROWNUM != 6) %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    182
                    4x
                    
                      
            ungroup() %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    183
                    4x
                    
                      
            mutate(

                    		
                  

                  

                    184
                    4x
                    
                      
                TOTAL = NA,

                    		
                  

                  

                    185
                    4x
                    
                      
                issue = "BCVA 1m check stops too early"

                    		
                  

                  

                    186
                    
                    
                      
            ) %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    187
                    4x
                    
                      
            select(all_of(output_variables), TOTAL, issue) %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    188
                    4x
                    
                      
            unique()

                    		
                  

                  

                    189
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    190
                    
                    
                      
        # subcheck 3: if BCVA 1m test has the correct total in eCRF

                    		
                  

                  

                    191
                    
                    
                      
        ## compare total and eCRF, output will include 1) totals in eCRF and calcualtion don't match

                    		
                  

                  

                    192
                    
                    
                      
        ## 2) total not recorded in eCRF 3) only total in eCRF, not test row/line read

                    		
                  

                  

                    193
                    4x
                    
                      
        anl_total <- BCVA_1m %>% filter(OESCAT %in% c("TOTAL", "NORMAL LIGHTING SCORE"))

                    		
                  

                  

                    194
                    4x
                    
                      
        anl_sum <- anl1 %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    195
                    4x
                    
                      
            group_by(USUBJID, VISIT, VISITNUM, OEDTC, OELOC, OELAT) %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    196
                    4x
                    
                      
            summarise(TOTAL = sum(OESTRESN), .groups = "drop") %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    197
                    4x
                    
                      
            ungroup()

                    		
                  

                  

                    198
                    4x
                    
                      
        incorrect1m <- anl_total %>% full_join(anl_sum, by = c("USUBJID", "VISIT", "VISITNUM", "OEDTC", "OELOC", "OELAT")) %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    199
                    4x
                    
                      
            filter(is.na(TOTAL) | is.na(OESTRESN) | OESTRESN != TOTAL) %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    200
                    4x
                    
                      
            filter(!(OESTRESN == 0 & is.na(TOTAL))) %>% ## filtered out when 1m is not done and total is 0

                    		
                  

                  

                    201
                    4x
                    
                      
            mutate(issue = "BCVA 1m score incorrect") %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    202
                    4x
                    
                      
            select(all_of(output_variables), TOTAL, issue) %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    203
                    4x
                    
                      
            unique()

                    		
                  

                  

                    204
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    205
                    
                    
                      
        ## rbind all three subchecks

                    		
                  

                  

                    206
                    4x
                    
                      
        df <- rbind(late1m, early1m, incorrect1m)

                    		
                  

                  

                    207
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    208
                    4x
                    
                      
        if (nrow(df) != 0) {

                    		
                  

                  

                    209
                    3x
                    
                      
            fail(paste0(nrow(df), " BCVA 1m test record(s) failed with 1) test stops too late 2) test stops too early 3) total incorrect. "), df)

                    		
                  

                  

                    210
                    
                    
                      
        } else {

                    		
                  

                  

                    211
                    1x
                    
                      
            pass()

                    		
                  

                  

                    212
                    
                    
                      
        }

                    		
                  

                  

                    213
                    
                    
                      
    }

                    		
                  

                  

                    214
                    
                    
                      
}

check_ec_sc_lat <- function(EC,SC) {

                    		
                  

                  

                    127
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    128
                    3x
                    
                      
    if (SC %lacks_any% c("USUBJID", "SCTEST", "SCTESTCD", "SCCAT", "SCORRES", "SCDTC")) {

                    		
                  

                  

                    129
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    130
                    !
                    
                      
        fail(lacks_msg(SC, c("USUBJID","SCTEST","SCTESTCD","SCCAT","SCORRES", "SCDTC")))

                    		
                  

                  

                    131
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    132
                    
                    
                      
    }

                    		
                  

                  

                    133
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    134
                    3x
                    
                      
    else if (EC %lacks_any% c("USUBJID", "ECMOOD", "ECSTDY", "VISIT", "ECSTDTC", "ECOCCUR", "ECROUTE")) {

                    		
                  

                  

                    135
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    136
                    1x
                    
                      
        fail(lacks_msg(EC, c("USUBJID", "ECMOOD", "ECSTDY", "VISIT", "ECSTDTC", "ECOCCUR", "ECROUTE")))

                    		
                  

                  

                    137
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    138
                    
                    
                      
    }

                    		
                  

                  

                    139
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    140
                    
                    
                      
    else {

                    		
                  

                  

                    141
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    142
                    
                    
                      
        # Filter for records where Study Drug was administered in the eye

                    		
                  

                  

                    143
                    2x
                    
                      
        EC <- EC %>% filter(ECROUTE %in% c("CONJUNCTIVAL","INTRACAMERAL", "INTRACORNEAL", 

                    		
                  

                  

                    144
                    2x
                    
                      
                                           "INTRAOCULAR","INTRAVITREAL", "OPHTHALMIC", 

                    		
                  

                  

                    145
                    2x
                    
                      
                                           "RETROBULBAR", "SUBRETINAL", 

                    		
                  

                  

                    146
                    2x
                    
                      
                                           "SUBTENON", "SUBCONJUNCTIVAL"))

                    		
                  

                  

                    147
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    148
                    
                    
                      
        # Check whether EC has any records where study drug was administered in the eye - if not then check passes

                    		
                  

                  

                    149
                    2x
                    
                      
        if (nrow(EC) == 0){

                    		
                  

                  

                    150
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    151
                    !
                    
                      
            pass()

                    		
                  

                  

                    152
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    153
                    
                    
                      
        }

                    		
                  

                  

                    154
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    155
                    
                    
                      
        else {

                    		
                  

                  

                    156
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    157
                    
                    
                      
            # Now that we know that Study drug is administered in the eye, check for ECLAT and ECLOC

                    		
                  

                  

                    158
                    2x
                    
                      
            if (EC %lacks_any% c("ECLAT", "ECLOC")) {

                    		
                  

                  

                    159
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    160
                    !
                    
                      
                fail(lacks_msg(EC, c("ECLAT", "ECLOC")))

                    		
                  

                  

                    161
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    162
                    
                    
                      
            }

                    		
                  

                  

                    163
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    164
                    
                    
                      
            # Subset SC data on SC.SCCAT = "STUDY EYE SELECTION", and

                    		
                  

                  

                    165
                    
                    
                      
            # SCTESTCD = "FOCID". SC.SCORRES OS (oculus sinister) means the left

                    		
                  

                  

                    166
                    
                    
                      
            # eye and OD (oculus dextrus) means the right eye.

                    		
                  

                  

                    167
                    2x
                    
                      
            SC <- SC %>% 

                    		
                  

                  

                    168
                    2x
                    
                      
                select(USUBJID, SCTESTCD, SCTEST, SCCAT, SCORRES, SCDTC) %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    169
                    2x
                    
                      
                filter(toupper(SCTESTCD) == "FOCID") %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    170
                    2x
                    
                      
                mutate(SC_STUDYEYE = ifelse(toupper(SCORRES) == "OS", "LEFT",

                    		
                  

                  

                    171
                    2x
                    
                      
                                            ifelse(toupper(SCORRES) == "OD", "RIGHT","SCORRES Value not OS or OD")))

                    		
                  

                  

                    172
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    173
                    
                    
                      
            # Subset EC data on EC.ECCAT (if available) remove Fellow Eye Records, 

                    		
                  

                  

                    174
                    
                    
                      
            # EC.ECMOOD = "PERFORMED" EC.ECOCCUR = "Y"

                    		
                  

                  

                    175
                    2x
                    
                      
            if (any(names(EC) == "ECCAT") == TRUE) {

                    		
                  

                  

                    176
                    2x
                    
                      
                EC <- EC %>% filter(toupper(ECMOOD) == "PERFORMED" & ECOCCUR == "Y" & 

                    		
                  

                  

                    177
                    2x
                    
                      
                                        toupper(ECLOC) == "EYE" & !grepl("FELLOW", ECCAT, ignore.case=TRUE))

                    		
                  

                  

                    178
                    
                    
                      
            }

                    		
                  

                  

                    179
                    !
                    
                      
            else if (any(names(EC) == "ECCAT") == FALSE) {

                    		
                  

                  

                    180
                    !
                    
                      
                EC <- EC %>% filter(toupper(ECMOOD) == "PERFORMED" & ECOCCUR == "Y" & 

                    		
                  

                  

                    181
                    !
                    
                      
                                        toupper(ECLOC) == "EYE")

                    		
                  

                  

                    182
                    
                    
                      
            }

                    		
                  

                  

                    183
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    184
                    2x
                    
                      
            perm_var <- c("ECCAT")

                    		
                  

                  

                    185
                    2x
                    
                      
            int_var <- intersect(names(EC), perm_var)

                    		
                  

                  

                    186
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    187
                    2x
                    
                      
            my_select_var <- c("USUBJID", int_var, "ECROUTE", "ECLOC", "ECMOOD", 

                    		
                  

                  

                    188
                    2x
                    
                      
                               "ECLAT", "ECSTDY", "VISIT", "ECSTDTC", "ECOCCUR")

                    		
                  

                  

                    189
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    190
                    2x
                    
                      
            EC <- EC[,my_select_var]

                    		
                  

                  

                    191
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    192
                    
                    
                      
            # Merge SC & EC by USUBJID & Create a variable when STUDYEYE do not match with ECLAT

                    		
                  

                  

                    193
                    2x
                    
                      
            mydf1 <- full_join(SC, EC, by="USUBJID") %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    194
                    2x
                    
                      
                mutate(MISFLAG = ifelse((toupper(SC_STUDYEYE) != toupper(ECLAT)) | is.na(toupper(ECLAT)) , 1, 0))

                    		
                  

                  

                    195
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    196
                    2x
                    
                      
            mydf = mydf1 %>% filter(MISFLAG == 1)%>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    197
                    2x
                    
                      
                filter(ECROUTE != "NON-OCULAR ROUTE" | is.na(ECROUTE)) %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    198
                    2x
                    
                      
                select(-MISFLAG, -SCTESTCD, -SCTEST, -SCCAT, -ECLOC, -ECMOOD, -ECOCCUR, -SCORRES)

                    		
                  

                  

                    199
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    200
                    2x
                    
                      
            if ((nrow(mydf) > 0 ) == FALSE) {

                    		
                  

                  

                    201
                    1x
                    
                      
                pass()

                    		
                  

                  

                    202
                    
                    
                      
            } else {

                    		
                  

                  

                    203
                    1x
                    
                      
                fail(paste0(nrow(mydf), " record(s) with Study Drug not administered in the Study Eye. "), mydf )

                    		
                  

                  

                    204

check_tr_trdtc_across_visit <- function(TR) {

                    		
                  

                  

                    32
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    33
                    
                    
                      
    ###First check that required variables exist and return a message if they don't

                    3x

                    35
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    36
                    1x
                    
                      
        fail(lacks_msg(TR, c("USUBJID", "TRDTC", "VISIT", "TRTESTCD")))

                    		
                  

                  

                    37
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    38
                    
                    
                      
    } else{

                    		
                  

                  

                    39
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    40
                    
                    
                      
        ### Find unique pairs of TRDTC and VISIT per USUBJID

                    		
                  

                  

                    41
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    42
                    2x
                    
                      
        if(TR %lacks_any% "TREVAL"){

                    		
                  

                  

                    43
                    2x
                    
                      
        trsub = TR %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    44
                    2x
                    
                      
            filter(TRTESTCD == "LDIAM") %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    45
                    2x
                    
                      
            select(USUBJID, TRDTC, VISIT, TRTESTCD)

                    		
                  

                  

                    46
                    
                    
                      
        }else{

                    		
                  

                  

                    47
                    !
                    
                      
        trsub = TR %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    48
                    !
                    
                      
            filter(TRTESTCD == "LDIAM" & (toupper(TREVAL) == "INVESTIGATOR" | is_sas_na(TREVAL))) %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    49
                    !
                    
                      
            select(USUBJID, TRDTC, VISIT, TRTESTCD)

                    		
                  

                  

                    50

                    51
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    52
                    2x
                    
                      
        if(nrow(trsub)>0){

                    		
                  

                  

                    53
                    2x
                    
                      
            mypairs = unique(trsub)

                    		
                  

                  

                    54
                    2x
                    
                      
            mypairs$x = 1

                    		
                  

                  

                    55
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    56
                    
                    
                      
            ### Get counts of visit values per date for each subject

                    		
                  

                  

                    57
                    2x

                    58
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    59
                    
                    
                      
            ### Subset where count is >1 and output

                    2x

                    66

                    68
                    2x
                    
                      
            rownames(mydf)=NULL

                    		
                  

                  

                    69
                    
                    
                      
        }else{

                    		
                  

                  

                    70

            mydf=data.frame()

                    		
                  

                  

                    71

                    72
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    73
                    
                    
                      
        ### if no consistency

                    		
                  

                  

                    74

        if (nrow(mydf)==0) {

                    		
                  

                  

                    75
                    1x
                    
                      
            pass()

#' @title Check if 1m BCVA test is completed per BCVA 4m result

                    		
                  

                  

                    2
                    
                    
                      
#'

                    		
                  

                  

                    3
                    
                    
                      
#' @description This ophthalmology function is to check if BCVA 1m test is done per BCVA 4m result.

                    		
                  

                  

                    4
                    
                    
                      
#' Patient, Visits, Laterality where Low Vision Tests were done are excluded from this check.

                    		
                  

                  

                    5
                    
                    
                      
#' 1> If 4m test total <= 19 and 1m test is not done.

                    		
                  

                  

                    6
                    
                    
                      
#' 2> If 4m test total >= 20 and 1m test is performed

                    		
                  

                  

                    7
                    
                    
                      
#' Above two conditions will be outputted in the final result data frame, which includes USUBJID, VISIT,

                    		
                  

                  

                    8
                    
                    
                      
#' OEDTC, OELAT, BCVA_4M_TOTAL, BCVA_1M_TOTAL, ISSUE.

                    		
                  

                  

                    9
                    
                    
                      
#' Please note that this check will assume that the BCVA 1m and 4m total are accurate and they happen on the same day.

                    		
                  

                  

                    10
                    
                    
                      
#' If they are happening on different dates, such records will be removed and not checked.

                    		
                  

                  

                    11
                    
                    
                      
#'

                    		
                  

                  

                    12
                    
                    
                      
#' @param OE Ophtho Dataset with variables USUBJID, OECAT, OESCAT, OETSTDTL, OESTRESN, OESTAT, OELAT,

                    		
                  

                  

                    13
                    
                    
                      
#' OERESCAT, VISIT, OEDTC, OEDY

                    		
                  

                  

                    14
                    
                    
                      
#'

                    		
                  

                  

                    15
                    
                    
                      
#' @importFrom dplyr %>% filter mutate select lag lead rename arrange summarise group_by ungroup

                    		
                  

                  

                    16
                    
                    
                      
#'

                    		
                  

                  

                    17
                    
                    
                      
#' @export

                    		
                  

                  

                    18
                    
                    
                      
#'

                    		
                  

                  

                    19
                    
                    
                      
#' @author Rosemary Li (HackR 2021 Team Eye)

                    		
                  

                  

                    20
                    
                    
                      
#'

                    		
                  

                  

                    21
                    
                    
                      
#' @examples

                    		
                  

                  

                    22
                    
                    
                      
#' OE_1m_done <- data.frame(

                    		
                  

                  

                    23
                    
                    
                      
#'   USUBJID = "1",

                    		
                  

                  

                    24
                    
                    
                      
#'   OECAT = "BEST CORRECTED VISUAL ACUITY",

                    		
                  

                  

                    25
                    
                    
                      
#'   OETSTDTL = c(rep("TESTING DISTANCE: 4M", 4), rep("TESTING DISTANCE: 1M", 3)),

                    		
                  

                  

                    26
                    
                    
                      
#'   OESCAT = c(rep("", 3), "TOTAL", rep("", 2), "TOTAL"),

                    		
                  

                  

                    27
                    
                    
                      
#'   OESTAT = rep("", 7),

                    		
                  

                  

                    28
                    
                    
                      
#'   OERESCAT = c("ROW 1 - SNELLEN 20/200", 

                    		
                  

                  

                    29
                    
                    
                      
#'                "ROW 2 - SNELLEN 20/160", 

                    		
                  

                  

                    30
                    
                    
                      
#'                "ROW 3 - SNELLEN 20/125", 

                    		
                  

                  

                    31
                    
                    
                      
#'                "",

                    		
                  

                  

                    32
                    
                    
                      
#'                "ROW 1 - SNELLEN 20/200", 

                    		
                  

                  

                    33
                    
                    
                      
#'                "ROW 2 - SNELLEN 20/160", 

                    		
                  

                  

                    34
                    
                    
                      
#'                ""),

                    		
                  

                  

                    35
                    
                    
                      
#'   VISIT = "WEEK 1",

                    		
                  

                  

                    36
                    
                    
                      
#'   VISITNUM = 5,

                    		
                  

                  

                    37
                    
                    
                      
#'   OEDTC = "2020-06-01",

                    		
                  

                  

                    38
                    
                    
                      
#'   OEDY = 8,

                    		
                  

                  

                    39
                    
                    
                      
#'   OELOC = "EYE",

                    		
                  

                  

                    40
                    
                    
                      
#'   OELAT = "LEFT",

                    		
                  

                  

                    41
                    
                    
                      
#'   OESTRESN = c(9, 9, 3, 21, 3, 2, 5)

                    		
                  

                  

                    42
                    
                    
                      
#' )

                    		
                  

                  

                    43
                    
                    
                      
#' check_oe_bcva_4m_vs_1m_req(OE_1m_done)

                    		
                  

                  

                    44
                    
                    
                      
#'

                    		
                  

                  

                    45
                    
                    
                      
#' OE_1m_not_done <- data.frame(

                    		
                  

                  

                    46
                    
                    
                      
#'   USUBJID = "1",

                    		
                  

                  

                    47
                    
                    
                      
#'   OECAT = "BEST CORRECTED VISUAL ACUITY",

                    		
                  

                  

                    48
                    
                    
                      
#'   OETSTDTL = "TESTING DISTANCE: 4M",

                    		
                  

                  

                    49
                    
                    
                      
#'   OESCAT = c(rep("", 3), "TOTAL"),

                    		
                  

                  

                    50
                    
                    
                      
#'   OESTAT = "",

                    		
                  

                  

                    51
                    
                    
                      
#'   OERESCAT = c("ROW 1 - SNELLEN 20/200", 

                    		
                  

                  

                    52
                    
                    
                      
#'                "ROW 2 - SNELLEN 20/160", 

                    		
                  

                  

                    53
                    
                    
                      
#'                "ROW 3 - SNELLEN 20/125", 

                    		
                  

                  

                    54
                    
                    
                      
#'                ""),

                    		
                  

                  

                    55
                    
                    
                      
#'   VISIT = "WEEK 1",

                    		
                  

                  

                    56
                    
                    
                      
#'   VISITNUM = 5,

                    		
                  

                  

                    57
                    
                    
                      
#'   OEDTC = "2020-06-01",

                    		
                  

                  

                    58
                    
                    
                      
#'   OEDY = 8,

                    		
                  

                  

                    59
                    
                    
                      
#'   OELOC = "EYE",

                    		
                  

                  

                    60
                    
                    
                      
#'   OELAT = "LEFT",

                    		
                  

                  

                    61
                    
                    
                      
#'   OESTRESN = c(5, 5, 2, 12)

                    		
                  

                  

                    62
                    
                    
                      
#' )

                    		
                  

                  

                    63
                    
                    
                      
#' check_oe_bcva_4m_vs_1m_req(OE_1m_not_done)

                    		
                  

                  

                    64
                    
                    
                      
#'

                    		
                  

                  

                    65
                    
                    
                      
check_oe_bcva_4m_vs_1m_req <- function(OE) {

                    		
                  

                  

                    66
                    4x
                    
                      
    required_variables <- c(

                    		
                  

                  

                    67
                    4x
                    
                      
        "USUBJID", "OECAT", "OESCAT", "OETSTDTL", "OESTAT", "OERESCAT", "VISIT", "VISITNUM", "OEDTC", "OEDY",

                    		
                  

                  

                    68
                    4x
                    
                      
         "OELAT", "OESTRESN"

                    		
                  

                  

                    69
                    
                    
                      
    )

                    		
                  

                  

                    70
                    4x
                    
                      
    output_variables <- c("USUBJID", "VISIT", "OEDTC", "OELAT", "BCVA_4M_TOTAL",

                    		
                  

                  

                    71
                    4x
                    
                      
                          "BCVA_1M_TOTAL", "ISSUE")

                    		
                  

                  

                    72
                    4x
                    
                      
    to_upper_variables <- function(variables) {

                    		
                  

                  

                    73
                    27x
                    
                      
        if(is.character(variables)) return(toupper(variables))

                    		
                  

                  

                    74
                    9x
                    
                      
        else return(variables)

                    		
                  

                  

                    75
                    
                    
                      
    }

                    		
                  

                  

                    76
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    77
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    78
                    4x
                    
                      
    if (OE %lacks_any% required_variables) {

                    		
                  

                  

                    79
                    1x
                    
                      
        fail(lacks_msg(OE, required_variables))

                    		
                  

                  

                    80
                    
                    
                      
    } else {

                    		
                  

                  

                    81
                    
                    
                      
        # preprocess OE dataset to get the relavent BCVA 4m and 1m data

                    		
                  

                  

                    82
                    
                    
                      
        ### select required variables

                    		
                  

                  

                    83
                    3x
                    
                      
        BCVA_4m_1m_total <- OE %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    84
                    3x
                    
                      
            select(all_of(required_variables))

                    		
                  

                  

                    85
                    
                    
                      
        ### convert character variables to upper case

                    		
                  

                  

                    86
                    3x
                    
                      
        for(var in required_variables){

                    		
                  

                  

                    87
                    36x
                    
                      
            BCVA_4m_1m_total[[var]]=to_upper_variables(BCVA_4m_1m_total[[var]])

                    		
                  

                  

                    88
                    
                    
                      
        }

                    		
                  

                  

                    89
                    
                    
                      
        ### filter on BCVA 4m and 1m criteria

                    		
                  

                  

                    90
                    3x
                    
                      
        BCVA_4m_1m_total <- BCVA_4m_1m_total %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    91
                    3x
                    
                      
            filter(OECAT == "BEST CORRECTED VISUAL ACUITY" &

                    		
                  

                  

                    92
                    3x
                    
                      
                       OETSTDTL %in% c('TESTING DISTANCE: 4M', 'TESTING DISTANCE: 1M') & OESTAT != "NOT DONE" &

                    		
                  

                  

                    93
                    3x
                    
                      
                       OESCAT %in% c("TOTAL", "NORMAL LIGHTING SCORE") & OESCAT != "LOW LUMINANCE") %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    94
                    3x
                    
                      
            select(USUBJID, VISIT, VISITNUM, OEDTC, OEDY, OELAT, OESTRESN, OETSTDTL)

                    		
                  

                  

                    95
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    96
                    
                    
                      
        ### Filter on Low Vision Tests & Get the Distinct list of Patient, VISIT, Laterality

                    		
                  

                  

                    97
                    
                    
                      
        # If Patient has done low vision test, 1m test req is not applicable.

                    		
                  

                  

                    98
                    3x
                    
                      
        BCVA_low_vision <- OE %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    99
                    3x
                    
                      
            filter(OECAT == "BEST CORRECTED VISUAL ACUITY" &

                    		
                  

                  

                    100
                    3x
                    
                      
                       OESCAT == "LOW VISION") %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    101
                    3x
                    
                      
            select(USUBJID, VISIT, VISITNUM, OEDTC, OEDY, OELAT)

                    		
                  

                  

                    102
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    103
                    3x
                    
                      
        BCVA_low_vision <- BCVA_low_vision %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    104
                    3x
                    
                      
            distinct(USUBJID, VISIT, VISITNUM, OEDTC, OEDY, OELAT) %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    105
                    3x
                    
                      
            mutate(lowvision_ind = 1)

                    		
                  

                  

                    106
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    107
                    
                    
                      
        # check if dates are unique for each USUBJID, VISITNUM, OELAT combination, if not, such a combination will be

                    		
                  

                  

                    108
                    
                    
                      
        # removed from the BCVA check including situations like 1) unscheduled visits on different dates, or 2) TOTAL

                    		
                  

                  

                    109
                    
                    
                      
        # date for 4m and 1m are recorded differently in the dataset.

                    		
                  

                  

                    110
                    3x
                    
                      
        nonunique_dates_for_each_sub_visit <- BCVA_4m_1m_total %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    111
                    3x
                    
                      
            group_by(USUBJID, VISIT, VISITNUM, OELAT) %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    112
                    3x
                    
                      
            summarise(num_of_dates = length(unique(OEDTC)), .groups = "drop") %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    113
                    3x
                    
                      
            filter(num_of_dates > 1) %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    114
                    3x
                    
                      
            ungroup()

                    		
                  

                  

                    115
                    3x
                    
                      
        BCVA_4m_1m_total <- BCVA_4m_1m_total %>% left_join(

                    		
                  

                  

                    116
                    3x
                    
                      
            nonunique_dates_for_each_sub_visit,

                    		
                  

                  

                    117
                    3x
                    
                      
            by = c("USUBJID", "VISIT", "VISITNUM", "OELAT")

                    		
                  

                  

                    118
                    
                    
                      
        ) %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    119
                    3x
                    
                      
            filter(is.na(num_of_dates)) %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    120
                    3x
                    
                      
            select( - num_of_dates)

                    		
                  

                  

                    121
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    122
                    
                    
                      
        ## Get BCVA 4m dataset

                    		
                  

                  

                    123
                    3x
                    
                      
        BCVA_4m <- BCVA_4m_1m_total %>% filter(OETSTDTL == "TESTING DISTANCE: 4M") %>% select(-OETSTDTL)

                    		
                  

                  

                    124
                    
                    
                      
        ## Get BCVA 4m dataset when result <= 19

                    		
                  

                  

                    125
                    3x
                    
                      
        BCVA_4m_19 <- BCVA_4m %>% filter(OESTRESN <= 19)

                    		
                  

                  

                    126
                    
                    
                      
        ## Get BCVA 4m dataset when result >= 20

                    		
                  

                  

                    127
                    3x
                    
                      
        BCVA_4m_20 <- BCVA_4m %>% filter(OESTRESN >= 20)

                    		
                  

                  

                    128
                    
                    
                      
        ## Get BCVA 1m dataset

                    		
                  

                  

                    129
                    3x
                    
                      
        BCVA_1m <- BCVA_4m_1m_total %>% filter(OETSTDTL == "TESTING DISTANCE: 1M") %>% select(-OETSTDTL)

                    		
                  

                  

                    130
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    131
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    132
                    
                    
                      
        # 4m test total <= 19 but 1m test not done

                    		
                  

                  

                    133
                    3x
                    
                      
        result19 <- BCVA_4m_19 %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    134
                    3x
                    
                      
            left_join(BCVA_1m, by = c("USUBJID", "VISIT", "VISITNUM", "OELAT", "OEDTC", "OEDY")) %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    135
                    3x
                    
                      
            rename(BCVA_4M_TOTAL = OESTRESN.x, BCVA_1M_TOTAL = OESTRESN.y) %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    136
                    3x
                    
                      
            filter(is.na(BCVA_1M_TOTAL) | (BCVA_1M_TOTAL == 0 & BCVA_4M_TOTAL <= 19)) %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    137
                    3x
                    
                      
            mutate(ISSUE = "1m Test Not Done but Required")

                    		
                  

                  

                    138
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    139
                    
                    
                      
        # Remove records when patients have completed low vision

                    		
                  

                  

                    140
                    3x
                    
                      
        result19 <- left_join(result19, BCVA_low_vision, by=c("USUBJID", "VISIT", "VISITNUM", "OELAT", "OEDTC", "OEDY")) %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    141
                    3x
                    
                      
            filter(is.na(lowvision_ind)) %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    142
                    3x
                    
                      
            select(-lowvision_ind)

                    		
                  

                  

                    143
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    144
                    
                    
                      
        # 4m test total >= 20 but 1m test done

                    		
                  

                  

                    145
                    3x
                    
                      
        result20 <- BCVA_4m_20 %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    146
                    3x
                    
                      
            left_join(BCVA_1m, by = c("USUBJID", "VISIT", "VISITNUM", "OELAT", "OEDTC", "OEDY")) %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    147
                    3x
                    
                      
            rename(BCVA_4M_TOTAL = OESTRESN.x, BCVA_1M_TOTAL = OESTRESN.y) %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    148
                    3x
                    
                      
            filter(!is.na(BCVA_1M_TOTAL)) %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    149
                    3x
                    
                      
            filter(BCVA_1M_TOTAL != 0) %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    150
                    3x
                    
                      
            mutate(ISSUE = "1m Test Done but Not Required")

                    		
                  

                  

                    151
                    
                    
                      
        # rbind two results

                    		
                  

                  

                    152
                    3x
                    
                      
        result <- rbind(result19, result20)

                    		
                  

                  

                    153
                    3x
                    
                      
        result <- result %>% select(-VISITNUM, -OEDY) # Remove VISITNUM & OEDY from final FAIL message

                    		
                  

                  

                    154
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    155
                    3x
                    
                      
        if (nrow(result) != 0) {

                    		
                  

                  

                    156
                    2x
                    
                      
            fail(paste0(nrow(result), " BCVA 1m test result(s) not done properly based on 4m result. "), result)

                    		
                  

                  

                    157
                    
                    
                      
        } else {

                    		
                  

                  

                    158
                    1x
                    
                      
            pass()

                    		
                  

                  

                    159
                    
                    
                      
        }

                    		
                  

                  

                    160
                    
                    
                      
    }

                    		
                  

                  

                    161
                    
                    
                      
}

#' @title Check that all TU  dates are duplicated or earlier than last

                    		
                  

                  

                    2
                    
                    
                      
#' visit's (possible datetime data entry error)

                    		
                  

                  

                    3
                    
                    
                      
#'

                    		
                  

                  

                    4
                    
                    
                      
#' @description This check identifies TUDTC values that are duplicated or

                    		
                  

                  

                    5
                    
                    
                      
#' earlier than last visit's. Unscheduled visits are excluded.

                    		
                  

                  

                    6
                    
                    
                      
#'

                    		
                  

                  

                    7
                    
                    
                      
#' @param TU Tumor Identification SDTM dataset with variables USUBJID,TUORRES ,TULOC, VISITNUM, VISIT, TUDTC, TUEVAL

                    		
                  

                  

                    8
                    
                    
                      
#'

                    		
                  

                  

                    9
                    
                    
                      
#' @return boolean value if check failed or passed with 'msg' attribute if the

                    		
                  

                  

                    10
                    
                    
                      
#'   test failed

                    		
                  

                  

                    11

                    12

                    13

                    18
                    
                    
                      
#' # no case

                    		
                  

                  

                    19
                    
                    
                      
#' TU <- data.frame(USUBJID = 101:102,

                    		
                  

                  

                    20
                    
                    
                      
#'                 TUORRES = rep(c("NEW", "TARGET"), 5),

                    		
                  

                  

                    21
