                    22
                    
                    
                      
#'                 TUDTC = rep(c("2017-01-01T08:25", "2017-01-05T09:25",

                    		
                  

                  

                    23
                    
                    
                      
#'                  "2017-01-15T10:25","2017-01-20T08:25","2017-01-25T08:25"), 2),

                    		
                  

                  

                    24
                    
                    
                      
#'                 VISITNUM = rep(1:5,2),

                    		
                  

                  

                    25
                    
                    
                      
#'                 VISIT = rep(c( "Visit 1", "Visit 2", "Visit 3", "Visit 4","VIsit 5"), 2),

                    		
                  

                  

                    26
                    
                    
                      
#'                 TUEVAL="INVESTIGATOR",

                    		
                  

                  

                    27
                    
                    
                      
#'                 stringsAsFactors = FALSE)

                    		
                  

                  

                    28
                    
                    
                      
#' check_tu_tudtc_visit_ordinal_error(TU)

                    		
                  

                  

                    29
                    
                    
                      
#'

                    		
                  

                  

                    30
                    
                    
                      
#' # adding cases with earler date

                    		
                  

                  

                    31
                    
                    
                      
#' TU$TUDTC[TU$USUBJID == 101 & TU$VISIT == "Visit 4"] <- "2017-01-10T08:25"

                    		
                  

                  

                    32
                    
                    
                      
#' TU$TUDTC[TU$USUBJID == 102 & TU$VISIT == "Visit 2"] <- "2017-01-01T06:25"

                    		
                  

                  

                    33
                    
                    
                      
#' check_tu_tudtc_visit_ordinal_error(TU)

                    		
                  

                  

                    34

                    35
                    
                    
                      
#' # adding cases with duplicated date

                    		
                  

                  

                    36
                    
                    
                      
#' TU$TUDTC[TU$USUBJID == 101 & TU$VISIT == "Visit 5"] <- "2017-01-10T08:25"

                    		
                  

                  

                    37

check_tu_tudtc_visit_ordinal_error <- function(TU){

                    		
                  

                  

                    42
                    4x
                    
                      
    class(TU) <- 'data.frame'

                    		
                  

                  

                    43
                    4x
                    
                      
    vars = c("USUBJID", "TUORRES","TULOC", "VISITNUM", "VISIT", "TUDTC","TUEVAL")

                    		
                  

                  

                    44
                    
                    
                      
    ### First check that required variables exist and return a message if they don't

                    		
                  

                  

                    45
                    4x
                    
                      
    if (TU %lacks_any% vars) {

                    		
                  

                  

                    46
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    47
                    1x
                    
                      
        fail(lacks_msg(TU, vars))

                    		
                  

                  

                    48
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    49
                    
                    
                      
    ### Dont run if VISITNUM is all missing

                    		
                  

                  

                    50
                    3x
                    
                      
    } else if (length(unique(TU[["VISITNUM"]]))<=1) {

                    		
                  

                  

                    51
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    52
                    !
                    
                      
        fail(msg="VISITNUM exists but only a single value. ")

                    		
                  

                  

                    53
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    54
                    
                    
                      
    }    else {

                    		
                  

                  

                    55
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    56
                    3x
                    
                      
        subsetdf = subset(TU, TU$TUEVAL=="INVESTIGATOR" & !grepl("UNSCHEDU",toupper(TU$VISIT)),)

                    		
                  

                  

                    57
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    58
                    3x
                    
                      
        if(nrow(subsetdf)>0){

                    		
                  

                  

                    59
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    60
                    3x
                    
                      
        mydf2 <- dtc_dupl_early(

                    		
                  

                  

                    61
                    3x
                    
                      
            dts = subsetdf,

                    		
                  

                  

                    62
                    3x
                    
                      
            vars = vars,

                    		
                  

                  

                    63
                    
                    
                      
            ### groupby variables used for grouping and visit.order derivation

                    		
                  

                  

                    64
                    3x
                    
                      
            groupby = vars[c(1, 2, 3)],

                    		
                  

                  

                    65
                    3x
                    
                      
            dtc = vars[6],

                    		
                  

                  

                    66
                    
                    
                      
            ### variables used for ordering before visit.order derivation

                    		
                  

                  

                    67
                    3x
                    
                      
            vars[1],

                    		
                  

                  

                    68
                    3x
                    
                      
            vars[2],

                    		
                  

                  

                    69
                    3x
                    
                      
            vars[3],

                    		
                  

                  

                    70
                    3x
                    
                      
            vars[4],

                    		
                  

                  

                    71
                    3x
                    
                      
            vars[5],

                    		
                  

                  

                    72
                    3x
                    
                      
            vars[6]

                    		
                  

                  

                    73
                    
                    
                      
        )

                    		
                  

                  

                    74
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    75
                    
                    
                      
        ### Subset if Vis_order not equal Dtc_order

                    		
                  

                  

                    76
                    3x
                    
                      
        myout <- mydf2[!is.na(mydf2$check.flag), ]

                    		
                  

                  

                    77
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    78

run_check = function(check,

                    		
                  

                  

                    55
                    
                    
                      
                     fxn_in,

                    		
                  

                  

                    56
                    
                    
                      
                     xls_title,

                    		
                  

                  

                    57
                    
                    
                      
                     pdf_title,

                    		
                  

                  

                    58
                    
                    
                      
                     pdf_subtitle,

                    		
                  

                  

                    59
                    
                    
                      
                     pdf_return,

                    		
                  

                  

                    60
                    
                    
                      
                     verbose){

                    		
                  

                  

                    61
                    
                    
                      
    

                    		
                  

                  

                    62
                    !
                    
                      
    if (verbose == TRUE) { # have to print in this workaround way since cat doesn't work while parallel processing

                    		
                  

                  

                    63
                    !
                    
                      
        system(sprintf('echo "%s"', paste0("Running:", check)))

                    		
                  

                  

                    64
                    
                    
                      
    }

                    		
                  

                  

                    65
                    
                    
                      
    

                    		
                  

                  

                    66
                    
                    
                      
    # run a data check

                    		
                  

                  

                    67
                    !
                    
                      
    result <-

                    		
                  

                  

                    68
                    !
                    
                      
        try(eval(parse(text = paste0(

                    		
                  

                  

                    69
                    !
                    
                      
            check, "(", fxn_in, ")"

                    		
                  

                  

                    70
                    !
                    
                      
        ))), silent = TRUE)

                    		
                  

                  

                    71
                    
                    
                      
    

                    		
                  

                  

                    72

                    73
                    !
                    
                      
    if (!is.null(attributes(result)$data) & !is.data.frame(attributes(result)$data)){

                    		
                  

                  

                    74
                    !
                    
                      
        warning(paste0(

                    		
                  

                  

                    75
                    !
                    
                      
            "\nReturned data are not a data frame for check: ",

                    		
                  

                  

                    76
                    !
                    
                      
            check,

                    		
                  

                  

                    77
                    
                    
                      
            "."

                    		
                  

                  

                    78

                    80
                    
                    
                      
    

                    		
                  

                  

                    81
                    
                    
                      
    # read the message, resulting dataset and other variables

                    		
                  

                  

                    82
                    !
                    
                      
    msg <- as.character(attributes(result)$msg)

                    		
                  

                  

                    83
                    !
                    
                      
    data <- as.data.frame(attributes(result)$data)

                    		
                  

                  

                    84
                    !
                    
                      
    xls_title <- substr(xls_title, start = 1, stop = 31)

                    		
                  

                  

                    85
                    !
                    
                      
    notes <- " "

                    		
                  

                  

                    86
                    
                    
                      
    

                    		
                  

                  

                    87
                    
                    
                      
    # determine n of recs in the data check dataset. This will be used for the summary page.

                    		
                  

                  

                    88
                    !
                    
                      
    if (any(grepl("try-error",class(result)))) {

                    		
                  

                  

                    89
                    !
                    
                      
        nrec = 0

                    		
                  

                  

                    90
                    !
                    
                      
        notes <-

                    		
                  

                  

                    91
                    !
                    
                      
            paste0("ATTENTION! Check was not run: ", pdf_return)

                    		
                  

                  

                    92
                    !
                    
                      
    } else if (is.null(attributes(result)$data)) {

                    		
                  

                  

                    93
                    !
                    
                      
        nrec <-

                    		
                  

                  

                    94
                    !
                    
                      
            0 # set to 0 if resulting dataset was not created in case where

                    		
                  

                  

                    95
                    
                    
                      
        # no bad records found or check failed due to missing variables.

                    		
                  

                  

                    96

        # if check failed due to missing variables then alert user

                    !
                    
                      
        if (result != TRUE)

                    		
                  

                  

                    99
                    !
                    
                      
            notes <-

                    50

                    52
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    53

                    54

                    56
                    !

      select("USUBJID","DTHFL","DTHDTC") %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    58
                    !

                    !
                    
                      
    if(nrow(mydf)==0){

                    		
                  

                  

                    64
                    !
                    
                      
      pass()

                    		
                  

                  

                    65
                    
                    
                      
      ### Return subset dataframe if there are records with potential data issue

                    		
                  

                  

                    66

    }else if(nrow(mydf)>0){

                    		
                  

                  

                    67
                    !

                    42

                    44
                    3x

                    45
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    46
                    1x
                    
                      
    fail(lacks_msg(PR, c("USUBJID", "PRTRT", "PRSTDTC")))

                    		
                  

                  

                    47
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    48
                    
                    
                      
    } else{

                    		
                  

                  

                    49
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    50
                    
                    
                      
      #Apply company specific preprocessing function

                    		
                  

                  

                    51
                    2x
                    
                      
      PR = preproc(PR,...)

                    		
                  

                  

                    52
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    53
                    
                    
                      
      # PRENDTC is an optional variable

                    		
                  

                  

                    54
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    55
                    2x
                    
                      
      if (PR %lacks_any% "PRENDTC") {

                    		
                  

                  

                    56
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    57
                    !
                    
                      
        mydf <- PR %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    58
                    !
                    
                      
          filter(missing_month(PRSTDTC)) %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    59
                    !
                    
                      
          select(any_of(c("USUBJID", "PRTRT", "PRSTDTC", "PRENDTC", "RAVE")))

                    		
                  

                  

                    60

                    62
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    63
                    2x
                    
                      
        mydf <- PR %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    64
                    2x
                    
                      
          filter(missing_month(PRSTDTC) | missing_month(PRENDTC)) %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    65
                    2x
                    
                      
          select(any_of(c("USUBJID", "PRTRT", "PRSTDTC", "PRENDTC", "RAVE")))

                    		
                  

                  

                    66
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    67

                    68

                    2x

                    72
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    73
                    2x
                    
                      
      if(nrow(mydf)==0){

                    		
                  

                  

                    74
                    1x
                    
                      
        pass()

                    		
                  

                  

                    75
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    76
                    
                    
                      
        ### Return subset dataframe if there are records with inconsistency

                    		
                  

                  

                    77
                    1x
                    
                      
      }else if(nrow(mydf)>0){

                    79
                    1x
                    
                      
          fail(paste(length(unique(mydf$USUBJID)),

check_ae_aeout_aeendtc_aedthdtc <- function(AE,preproc=identity,...) {

                    		
                  

                  

                    50
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    51
                    5x
                    
                      
    if (AE %lacks_any% c("USUBJID", "AETERM", "AEENDTC", "AEDTHDTC", "AEOUT")) {

                    		
                  

                  

                    52
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    53
                    1x
                    
                      
        fail(lacks_msg(AE, c("USUBJID", "AETERM", "AEENDTC", "AEDTHDTC", "AEOUT" )))

                    		
                  

                  

                    54
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    55
                    
                    
                      
    }else {

                    		
                  

                  

                    56
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    57
                    
                    
                      
        #Apply company specific preprocessing function

                    		
                  

                  

                    58
                    4x
                    
                      
        AE = preproc(AE,...)

                    		
                  

                  

                    59
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    60
                    4x
                    
                      
            mydf <- AE %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    61
                    4x
                    
                      
                select(any_of(c("USUBJID", "AETERM", "AEENDTC", "AEDTHDTC", "AEOUT", "RAVE"))) %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    62
                    4x
                    
                      
                filter(AEOUT == 'FATAL') %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    63
                    4x
                    
                      
                filter(AEENDTC != AEDTHDTC | is_sas_na(AEENDTC))

                    		
                  

                  

                    64
                    4x
                    
                      
            rownames(mydf)=NULL

                    		
                  

                  

                    65
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    66
                    
                    
                      
       ## Add note

                    		
                  

                  

                    67
                    4x
                    
                      
        mydf$NOTE <- "**QUERY ONLY IF TEAM AGREES**"

                    		
                  

                  

                    68
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    69
                    4x
                    
                      
        if( nrow(mydf) > 0 ){

                    		
                  

                  

                    70
                    4x
                    
                      
            fail(paste(nrow(mydf), " AE(s) with AEOUT = 'FATAL' but AEDTHDTC and AEENDTC inconsistent. ",sep=""),

                    		
                  

                  

                    71
                    4x
                    
                      
            mydf)

                    		
                  

                  

                    72
                    
                    
                      
        } else {

                    		
                  

                  

                    73
                    !
                    
                      
            pass() # pass if AEOUT is FATAL but AEDTHDTC and AEENDTC are consistent

                    		
                  

                  

                    74
                    
                    
                      
        }

    }

                    		
                  

                  

                    76

                    36
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    37
                    
                    
                      
    # Checks if required variables are present

                    		
                  

                  

                    38
                    9x
                    
                      
    if (AE %lacks_any% c("USUBJID", "AEDTHDTC", "AESDTH", "AEDECOD", "AESTDTC")) {

                    		
                  

                  

                    39
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    40
                    !

                    45
                    8x
                    
                      
        AE = preproc(AE,...)

                    		
                  

                  

                    46
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    47
                    
                    
                      
        # Rows where AESDTH is "Y"

                    8x

        # Rows where AEDTHDTC is NA

check_dm_age_missing <- function(DM){

                    		
                  

                  

                    29
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    30
                    
                    
                      
  ###First check that required variables exist and return a message if they don't

                    		
                  

                  

                    31
                    !
                    
                      
  if(DM %lacks_any% c("USUBJID","AGE")){

                    		
                  

                  

                    32
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    33
                    !
                    
                      
      fail(lacks_msg(DM, c("USUBJID","AGE")))

                    		
                  

                  

                    34
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    35
                    
                    
                      
  }else{

                    		
                  

                  

                    36
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    37
                    
                    
                      
    ### Subset DM to only records with missing AGE

                    		
                  

                  

                    38
                    !
                    
                      
    mydf_0 = subset(DM, is_sas_na(DM$AGE), c("USUBJID","AGE"))

                    		
                  

                  

                    39
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    40
                    
                    
                      
    ### Subset DM to only records with AGE<18

                    		
                  

                  

                    41
                    !
                    
                      
    mydf_1 = subset(DM, !is_sas_na(DM$AGE) & DM$AGE<18, c("USUBJID","AGE"))

                    		
                  

                  

                    42
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    43
                    
                    
                      
    ### Subset DM to only records with AGE>90

                    		
                  

                  

                    44
                    !
                    
                      
    mydf_2 = subset(DM, !is_sas_na(DM$AGE) & DM$AGE>=90, c("USUBJID","AGE"))

                    		
                  

                  

                    45
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    46
                    
                    
                      
    ### Combine records with abnormal AGE

                    		
                  

                  

                    47
                    !
                    
                      
    mydf3 = rbind(mydf_0, mydf_1, mydf_2)

                    		
                  

                  

                    48
                    !
                    
                      
    mydf = mydf3[order(mydf3$USUBJID),]

                    		
                  

                  

                    49
                    !
                    
                      
    rownames(mydf)=NULL

                    		
                  

                  

                    50
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    51
                    
                    
                      
    ###Print to report

                    		
                  

                  

                    52
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    53
                    
                    
                      
    ### Return message if no records with missing AGE, AGE<18 or AGE>90

                    		
                  

                  

                    54
                    !
                    
                      
    if(nrow(mydf)==0){

                    		
                  

                  

                    55
                    !
                    
                      
      pass()

                    		
                  

                  

                    56
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    57
                    
                    
                      
      ### Return subset dataframe if there are records with missing AGE, AGE<18 or AGE>90

                    		
                  

                  

                    58
                    !
                    
                      
    }else if(nrow(mydf)>0){

                    		
                  

                  

                    59
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    60
                    !
                    
                      
        fail(paste("DM has ",length(unique(mydf$USUBJID)),

                    		
                  

                  

                    61
                    !
                    
                      
                   " patient(s) with suspicious age value(s). ",sep=""),

                    		
                  

                  

                    62
                    !
                    
                      
             mydf)

                    		
                  

                  

                    63
                    
                    
                      
        }

                    		
                  

                  

                    64
                    
                    
                      
  }

                    		
                  

                  

                    65
                    
                    
                      
}

check_ae_aeacn_ds_disctx_covid <- function(AE,DS,covid_df = NULL){

                    		
                  

                  

                    50
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    51
                    2x
                    
                      
    if(is.null(covid_df)){

                    		
                  

                  

                    52
                    
                    
                      
       

                    		
                  

                  

                    53
                    !
                    
                      
        fail("Did not detect Covid-19 Preferred Terms") 

                    		
                  

                  

                    54
                    
                    
                      
        

                    		
                  

                  

                    55
                    2x
                    
                      
    }else if( AE %lacks_any% c("USUBJID", "AETERM", "AEDECOD", "AESTDTC","AEACN")){

                    		
                  

                  

                    56
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    57
                    !
                    
                      
        fail(lacks_msg(AE, c("USUBJID", "AETERM", "AEDECOD", "AESTDTC","AEACN")))

                    		
                  

                  

                    58
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    59
                    2x
                    
                      
    }else if( DS %lacks_any% c("USUBJID","DSSPID","DSCAT","DSDECOD")){

                    		
                  

                  

                    60
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    61
                    !
                    
                      
        fail(lacks_msg(DS, c("USUBJID","DSSPID","DSCAT","DSDECOD")))

                    		
                  

                  

                    62
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    63
                    
                    
                      
    } else{

                    		
                  

                  

                    64
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    65
                    
                    
                      
        # keep COVID-19 AEs on which we want to check action taken with treatment

                    		
                  

                  

                    66
                    2x
                    
                      
        ae_covid <- merge(x = AE, y = covid_df,

                    		
                  

                  

                    67
                    2x
                    
                      
                          by.x = toupper("AEDECOD"), by.y = toupper("REFTERM"))

                    		
                  

                  

                    68
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    69
                    
                    
                      
        # keep columns that are needed

                    		
                  

                  

                    70
                    2x
                    
                      
        ae0 <- subset(ae_covid,

                    		
                  

                  

                    71
                    2x
                    
                      
                      select = c("USUBJID", "AEDECOD", "AESTDTC", "AEACN",

                    		
                  

                  

                    72
                    2x
                    
                      
                                 grep("AEACN[0-9]", names(AE), value=TRUE)))

                    		
                  

                  

                    73
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    74
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    75
                    
                    
                      
        # find how many AEACNx variables are in AE

                    		
                  

                  

                    76
                    2x
                    
                      
        aeacnvars <- grep("AEACN[0-9]", names(ae0), value=TRUE)

                    		
                  

                  

                    77
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    78
                    
                    
                      
        #create a where condition for AE based on count of AEACNx

                    		
                  

                  

                    79
                    2x
                    
                      
        whrcond <- paste("AEACN=='DRUG WITHDRAWN'")

                    		
                  

                  

                    80
                    2x
                    
                      
        for (i in aeacnvars) {

                    		
                  

                  

                    81
                    !
                    
                      
            whrcond <- paste(whrcond, " | ", i, "=='DRUG WITHDRAWN'", sep="")

                    		
                  

                  

                    82
                    
                    
                      
        }

                    		
                  

                  

                    83
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    84
                    
                    
                      
        # loop through each AEACNx and keep DRUG WITHDRAWN AEs

                    		
                  

                  

                    85
                    2x
                    
                      
        ae1 <- subset(ae0,

                    		
                  

                  

                    86
                    2x
                    
                      
                      eval(parse(text = whrcond)) )

                    		
                  

                  

                    87
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    88
                    
                    
                      
        # keep records with discontinuation treatment due to AE

                    		
                  

                  

                    89
                    2x
                    
                      
        ds0 <- subset(DS,

                    		
                  

                  

                    90
                    2x
                    
                      
                      DSCAT == 'DISPOSITION EVENT' & grepl("DISCTX", DSSPID) & DSDECOD == 'ADVERSE EVENT',

                    		
                  

                  

                    91
                    2x
                    
                      
                      select = c("USUBJID", "DSDECOD"))

                    		
                  

                  

                    92
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    93
                    
                    
                      
        # merge AE and DS

                    		
                  

                  

                    94
                    2x
                    
                      
        finout <- merge(x = ae1, y = ds0,

                    		
                  

                  

                    95
                    2x
                    
                      
                        by= "USUBJID",

                    		
                  

                  

                    96
                    2x
                    
                      
                        all.x = T)

                    		
                  

                  

                    97
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    98
                    
                    
                      
        # keep if only in AE and not found in DS

                    		
                  

                  

                    99
                    2x
                    
                      
        mydf <- subset(finout,

                    		
                  

                  

                    100
                    2x
                    
                      
                       is_sas_na(DSDECOD),

                    		
                  

                  

                    101
                    2x
                    
                      
                       select = -c(DSDECOD)

                    		
                  

                  

                    102
                    
                    
                      
        )

                    		
                  

                  

                    103
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    104
                    
                    
                      
        # Drop AEACN if its multiple

                    		
                  

                  

                    105
                    2x
                    
                      
        if("AEACN" %in% names(AE) & any(AE$AEACN=="MULTIPLE")){

                    		
                  

                  

                    106
                    !
                    
                      
            mydf$AEACN=NULL

                    		
                  

                  

                    107
                    
                    
                      
        }

                    		
                  

                  

                    108
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    109
                    2x
                    
                      
        rownames(mydf)=NULL

                    		
                  

                  

                    110
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    111
                    
                    
                      
        ### Return message if no inconsistency between AE and DS

                    		
                  

                  

                    112
                    2x
                    
                      
        if(nrow(mydf)==0){

                    		
                  

                  

                    113
                    1x
                    
                      
            pass()

                    		
                  

                  

                    114
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    115
                    
                    
                      
            ### Return subset dataframe if there are records with inconsistency

                    		
                  

                  

                    116
                    1x
                    
                      
        }else if(nrow(mydf)>0){

                    		
                  

                  

                    117
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    118
                    1x
                    
                      
            return(fail(paste(length(unique(mydf$USUBJID)),

                    		
                  

                  

                    119
                    1x
                    
                      
                              " patient(s) with COVID-19 AE indicating drug withdrawn but no Treatment Discon form indicating AE. ",sep=""), mydf))

                    		
                  

                  

                    120
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    121
                    
                    
                      
        } #end else if mydf>0

                    		
                  

                  

                    122
                    
                    
                      
    }  # end else if all required vars present

                    		
                  

                  

                    123
                    
                    
                      
} # end function

check_dd_ae_aeout_aedthdtc <- function(AE, preproc=identity,...) {

                    		
                  

                  

                    51
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    52
                    9x
                    
                      
    if (AE %lacks_any% c("USUBJID", "AEDTHDTC", "AEOUT", "AEDECOD", "AESTDTC")) {

                    		
                  

                  

                    53
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    54
                    !
                    
                      
        fail(lacks_msg(AE, c("USUBJID", "AEDTHDTC", "AEOUT", "AEDECOD", "AESTDTC")))

                    		
                  

                  

                    55
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    56
                    
                    
                      
    } else{

                    		
                  

                  

                    57
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    58
                    
                    
                      
        #Apply company specific preprocessing function

                    		
                  

                  

                    59
                    8x
                    
                      
        AE = preproc(AE,...)

                    		
                  

                  

                    60
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    61
                    
                    
                      
        # check if AEOUT=='FATAL' that there is a corresponding AEDTHDTC, death date

                    		
                  

                  

                    62
                    8x
                    
                      
        mydf <- unique(subset(AE

                    		
                  

                  

                    63
                    8x
                    
                      
                              , (AE$AEOUT == 'FATAL' & is_sas_na(AE$AEDTHDTC))

                    		
                  

                  

                    64
                    8x
                    
                      
                               | (!is_sas_na(AE$AEDTHDTC) & AE$AEOUT != 'FATAL')

                    		
                  

                  

                    65
                    
                    
                      
                              , )) %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    66
                    8x
                    
                      
            select(any_of(c("USUBJID", "AEDECOD", "AESTDTC","AEDTHDTC", "AEOUT","RAVE")))

                    		
                  

                  

                    67
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    68
                    
                    
                      
        # declare number of patients

                    		
                  

                  

                    69
                    8x
                    
                      
        n3 <- paste0('There are ', nrow(mydf), ' patients with a discrepant AE outcome and death date. ')

                    		
                  

                  

                    70
                    8x
                    
                      
        if (nrow(mydf) > 0) {

                    		
                  

                  

                    71
                    4x
                    
                      
            fail(n3, mydf)

                    		
                  

                  

                    72
                    4x
                    
                      
        } else if (nrow(mydf) == 0) {

                    		
                  

                  

                    73
                    4x
                    
                      
            pass()

                    		
                  

                  

                    74
                    
                    
                      
        }

                    		
                  

                  

                    75
                    
                    
                      
    }

                    		
                  

                  

                    76
                    
                    
                      
}

check_cm_cmdecod <- function(CM,preproc=identity,...){

                    		
                  

                  

                    49
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    50
                    
                    
                      
  ###First check that required variables exist and return a message if they don't

                    		
                  

                  

                    51
                    4x
                    
                      
  if(CM %lacks_any% c("USUBJID","CMTRT","CMDECOD","CMCAT")){

                    		
                  

                  

                    52
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    53
                    1x
                    
                      
    fail(lacks_msg(CM, c("USUBJID","CMTRT","CMDECOD","CMCAT")))

                    		
                  

                  

                    54
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    55
                    
                    
                      
  }else {

                    		
                  

                  

                    56
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    57
                    
                    
                      
    #Apply company specific pre-processing function

                    		
                  

                  

                    58
                    3x
                    
                      
    CM = preproc(CM,...)

                    		
                  

                  

                    59
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    60
                    
                    
                      
    ### Subset domain to only records with missing coded term (CMDECOD)

                    		
                  

                  

                    61
                    3x
                    
                      
    mydf <- CM %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    62
                    3x
                    
                      
      filter(grepl("CONCOMITANT",CMCAT)) %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    63
                    3x
                    
                      
      select(any_of(c("USUBJID", "CMSEQ","CMSTDTC","CMTRT","CMDECOD", "CMPRESP", "CMOCCUR", "RAVE"))) %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    64
                    3x
                    
                      
      filter(is_sas_na(CMDECOD))

                    		
                  

                  

                    65
                    3x
                    
                      
    rownames(mydf)=NULL

                    		
                  

                  

                    66
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    67
                    
                    
                      
    ###Print to report

                    		
                  

                  

                    68
                    
                    
                      
    ### Return message if no records with missing CMDECOD

                    		
                  

                  

                    69
                    3x
                    
                      
    if(nrow(mydf)==0){

                    		
                  

                  

                    70
                    1x
                    
                      
      pass()

                    		
                  

                  

                    71
                    
                    
                      
      ### Return subset dataframe if there are records with missing CMDECOD

                    		
                  

                  

                    72
                    2x
                    
                      
    }else if(nrow(mydf)>0){

                    		
                  

                  

                    73
                    2x
                    
                      
      fail(paste("CM has ",nrow(mydf)," record(s) with missing CMDECOD. ",

                    		
                  

                  

                    74
                    2x
                    
                      
                 sep=""), mydf)

                    		
                  

                  

                    75
                    
                    
                      
    }

                    		
                  

                  

                    76
                    
                    
                      
  }

                    		
                  

                  

                    77
                    
                    
                      
}

check_tr_dup <- function(TR){

                    		
                  

                  

                    33
                    4x
                    
                      
    if (TR %lacks_any% c("USUBJID","TRCAT","TRTESTCD","TRDTC","TRSTRESC")){

                    		
                  

                  

                    34
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    35
                    1x
                    
                      
        fail (lacks_msg(TR, c("USUBJID","TRCAT","TRTESTCD","TRDTC","TRSTRESC")))

                    		
                  

                  

                    36
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    37
                    3x
                    
                      
    } else if (TR %lacks_all% c("TRLINKID","TRLNKID")) {

                    		
                  

                  

                    38
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    39
                    1x
                    
                      
        fail("TR is missing both the TRLINKID and TRLNKID variable. ")

                    		
                  

                  

                    40
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    41
                    
                    
                      
    } else{

                    		
                  

                  

                    42
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    43
                    2x
                    
                      
        myvars <- c("USUBJID","TRCAT","TRTESTCD",names(TR)[names(TR) %in% c("TRLINKID","TRLNKID")],names(TR)[names(TR) %in% "TRSPID"],"TRDTC","TRSTRESC")

                    		
                  

                  

                    44
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    45
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    46
                    2x
                    
                      
        if(TR %lacks_any% "TREVAL"){

                    		
                  

                  

                    47
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    48
                    
                    
                      
        # leave only variabls on which we want to check duplicate TR records

                    		
                  

                  

                    49
                    2x
                    
                      
        tr1 <- TR %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    50
                    2x
                    
                      
            arrange_at(myvars) %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    51
                    2x
                    
                      
            select(any_of(myvars))

                    		
                  

                  

                    52
                    
                    
                      
        }else{

                    		
                  

                  

                    53
                    !
                    
                      
            tr1 <- TR %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    54
                    !
                    
                      
                arrange_at(myvars) %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    55
                    !
                    
                      
                filter(toupper(TREVAL) == "INVESTIGATOR" | is_sas_na(TREVAL)) %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    56
                    !
                    
                      
                select(any_of(myvars))

                    		
                  

                  

                    57
                    
                    
                      
        }

                    		
                  

                  

                    58
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    59
                    
                    
                      
        # check if there are duplicate TR records

                    		
                  

                  

                    60
                    2x
                    
                      
        dups <- subset(tr1,duplicated(tr1),myvars)

                    		
                  

                  

                    61
                    2x
                    
                      
        rownames(dups)=NULL

                    		
                  

                  

                    62
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    63
                    
                    
                      
        # declare number of duplicated AEs and print them

                    		
                  

                  

                    64
                    2x
                    
                      
        n0 <- paste('There are ', nrow(dups), ' duplicated TR records. ', sep ='')

                    		
                  

                  

                    65
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    66
                    2x
                    
                      
        if (nrow(dups) == 0){

                    		
                  

                  

                    67
                    1x
                    
                      
            pass()

                    		
                  

                  

                    68
                    
                    
                      
        } else{

                    		
                  

                  

                    69
                    1x
                    
                      
            fail(

                    		
                  

                  

                    70
                    1x
                    
                      
                paste(n0), data=dups

                    		
                  

                  

                    71
                    
                    
                      
            )

        }

                    		
                  

                  

                    73
                    
                    
                      
    }

                    		
                  

                  

                    74

                    58
                    !
