check_ex_dup <- function(EX){

                    		
                  

                  

                    62
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    63
                    
                    
                      
  ###First bifurcate EX into a df based on occurrence of EXOCCUR

                    		
                  

                  

                    64
                    8x
                    
                      
  if ("EXOCCUR" %in% names(EX)) {

                    		
                  

                  

                    65
                    7x
                    
                      
    EX <- EX %>% filter(EXOCCUR == "Y")

                    		
                  

                  

                    66
                    
                    
                      
  }

                    		
                  

                  

                    67
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    68
                    
                    
                      
  ###Check that required variables exist and return a message if they don't

                    		
                  

                  

                    69
                    7x
                    
                      
  if(EX %lacks_any% c("USUBJID", "EXTRT", "EXDOSE", "EXSTDTC")){

                    		
                  

                  

                    70
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    71
                    !
                    
                      
      fail(lacks_msg(EX, c("USUBJID", "EXTRT", "EXDOSE", "EXSTDTC")))

                    		
                  

                  

                    72
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    73
                    
                    
                      
  } else{

                    		
                  

                  

                    74
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    75
                    
                    
                      
    # leave only variables on which we want to check duplicate dosing

                    		
                  

                  

                    76
                    7x
                    
                      
    ex0 <- subset(EX, select = c("USUBJID", "EXTRT", "EXDOSE", "EXSTDTC"))

                    		
                  

                  

                    77
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    78
                    
                    
                      
    # sort

                    		
                  

                  

                    79
                    7x
                    
                      
    ex1 <- with(ex0, ex0[order(USUBJID, EXTRT, EXDOSE, EXSTDTC),])

                    		
                  

                  

                    80
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    81
                    
                    
                      
    # check if there are duplicate dosing

                    		
                  

                  

                    82
                    7x
                    
                      
    dups <- subset(ex1,duplicated(ex1),c("USUBJID", "EXTRT", "EXDOSE", "EXSTDTC"))

                    		
                  

                  

                    83
                    7x
                    
                      
    rownames(dups)=NULL

                    		
                  

                  

                    84
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    85
                    7x
                    
                      
    n0 <- ''; n1 <- '';

                    		
                  

                  

                    86
                    
                    
                      
    # declare number of duplicated dosing and print them

                    		
                  

                  

                    87
                    7x
                    
                      
    n0 <- paste('There are ', nrow(dups), ' duplicated exposure records. ', sep ='')

                    		
                  

                  

                    88
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    89
                    7x
                    
                      
    if(nrow(dups)>0){

                    		
                  

                  

                    90
                    
                    
                      
      ## check that the visit variable is in the dataset

                    		
                  

                  

                    91
                    3x
                    
                      
      if(EX %lacks_any% "VISIT"){

                    		
                  

                  

                    92
                    
                    
                      
        #print this list without visit information appended if there is no visit variable

                    		
                  

                  

                    93
                    3x
                    
                      
          fail(

                    		
                  

                  

                    94
                    3x
                    
                      
              msg = n0,

                    		
                  

                  

                    95
                    3x
                    
                      
              data = dups

                    		
                  

                  

                    96
                    
                    
                      
          )

                    		
                  

                  

                    97
                    
                    
                      
      } else{

                    		
                  

                  

                    98
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    99
                    
                    
                      
        # merge this back to get the visit to print in the duplicate list

                    		
                  

                  

                    100
                    !
                    
                      
        ex2 <- subset(EX, select = c("USUBJID","EXTRT","EXDOSE","EXSTDTC","VISIT"))

                    		
                  

                  

                    101
                    
                    
                      
        # sort

                    		
                  

                  

                    102
                    !
                    
                      
        ex2s <- with(ex2, ex2[order(USUBJID, EXTRT, EXDOSE, EXSTDTC, VISIT),])

                    		
                  

                  

                    103
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    104
                    
                    
                      
        # left join to merge on VISIT

                    		
                  

                  

                    105
                    !
                    
                      
        dupswithvisit <- merge(x=dups, y=ex2s, by=c("USUBJID","EXTRT","EXDOSE","EXSTDTC"), all.x=TRUE)

                    		
                  

                  

                    106
                    !
                    
                      
        dupswithvisit = unique(dupswithvisit)

                    		
                  

                  

                    107
                    
                    
                      
        #print this list with visit appended

                    		
                  

                  

                    108
                    !
                    
                      
        fail(

                    		
                  

                  

                    109
                    !
                    
                      
            msg = n0,

                    		
                  

                  

                    110
                    !
                    
                      
            data = dupswithvisit

                    		
                  

                  

                    111
                    
                    
                      
        )

                    		
                  

                  

                    112
                    
                    
                      
      }

                    		
                  

                  

                    113
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    114
                    4x
                    
                      
    } else if(nrow(dups)==0){

                    		
                  

                  

                    115
                    4x
                    
                      
        pass()

                    		
                  

                  

                    116
                    
                    
                      
    }

                    		
                  

                  

                    117
                    
                    
                      
  }

                    		
                  

                  

                    118
                    
                    
                      
}

                    47

                    4x

check_dm_usubjid_dup <- function(DM) {

                    		
                  

                  

                    73
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    74
                    11x
                    
                      
    if (DM %lacks_any% "USUBJID") {

                    		
                  

                  

                    75
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    76
                    1x
                    
                      
        fail(lacks_msg(DM, "USUBJID"))

                    		
                  

                  

                    77
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    78
                    
                    
                      
    } else {

                    		
                  

                  

                    79
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    80
                    9x
                    
                      
        DM2 <- select(DM, USUBJID)

                    		
                  

                  

                    81
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    82
                    
                    
                      
        # Identify duplicate USUBJID

                    		
                  

                  

                    83
                    9x

                    84
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    85
                    
                    
                      
        # Derive patient number for USUBJID not identified as duplicates

                    		
                  

                  

                    86
                    9x

                    87
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    88
                    
                    
                      
        # Identify duplicate patient numbers across different USUBJIDs

                    		
                  

                  

                    89
                    9x
                    
                      
        DM3 <- group_by(DM2, subject_id) %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    90
                    9x
                    
                      
            mutate(n = n()) %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    91
                    9x
                    
                      
            ungroup()

                    		
                  

                  

                    92
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    93
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    94
                    9x
                    
                      
        DM3$FLAG <- ifelse(DM3$FLAG == "" & DM3$n > 1, "Same Patient Number Across Different USUBJID", DM3$FLAG)

                    		
                  

                  

                    95
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    96
                    9x
                    
                      
        DM4 <- filter(DM3, FLAG != "") %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    97
                    9x
                    
                      
            select(-c(subject_id, n))

                    		
                  

                  

                    98
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    99
                    9x
                    
                      
        if (nrow(DM4) > 0) {

                    		
                  

                  

                    100

                    4x

check_ds_dsscat <- function(DS){

                    		
                  

                  

                    34
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    35
                    !
                    
                      
    if (DS %lacks_any% c("USUBJID","DSSCAT")) {

                    		
                  

                  

                    36
                    !
                    
                      
        fail(lacks_msg(DS, c("USUBJID","DSSCAT")))

                    		
                  

                  

                    37
                    
                    
                      
    } else{

                    		
                  

                  

                    38
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    39
                    !
                    
                      
        myds <- DS %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    40
                    !
                    
                      
            select("USUBJID","DSSCAT") %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    41
                    !
                    
                      
            filter(grepl("STUDY", toupper(DSSCAT))

                    		
                  

                  

                    42
                    !
                    
                      
                   & grepl("DISCON", toupper(DSSCAT))

                    		
                  

                  

                    43
                    !
                    
                      
                   & !grepl("DRUG", toupper(DSSCAT))

                    		
                  

                  

                    44
                    !
                    
                      
                   & !grepl("TREATMENT", toupper(DSSCAT)))

                    		
                  

                  

                    45
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    46
                    !
                    
                      
        if(nrow(myds)==0){

                    		
                  

                  

                    47
                    !
                    
                      
            fail(paste("There are no study discontinuation records"))

                    		
                  

                  

                    48
                    
                    
                      
        } else{

                    		
                  

                  

                    49
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    50
                    !
                    
                      
            n_uniqueID <- length(unique(myds$USUBJID))

                    		
                  

                  

                    51
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    52
                    
                    
                      
            #gives you a data frame with a list of ID and the frequency they occured

                    		
                  

                  

                    53
                    !
                    
                      
            n_occur <-data.frame (table(myds$USUBJID))

                    		
                  

                  

                    54
                    !
                    
                      
            colnames(n_occur) = c("USUBJID","Freq")

                    		
                  

                  

                    55
                    !
                    
                      
            IDlist <- subset(n_occur,n_occur$Freq>1)

                    		
                  

                  

                    56
                    !
                    
                      
            myrecs = merge(myds, subset(IDlist,,select=c("USUBJID")),

                    		
                  

                  

                    57
                    !
                    
                      
                           by ="USUBJID",all.y=TRUE )

                    		
                  

                  

                    58
                    !
                    
                      
            colnames(IDlist) <- c("Duplicate USUBJID", "Number of Records")

                    		
                  

                  

                    59
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    60
                    !
                    
                      
            if (n_uniqueID== nrow(myds)){

                    		
                  

                  

                    61
                    !
                    
                      
                pass()

                    		
                  

                  

                    62
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    63
                    !
                    
                      
            } else if (n_uniqueID != nrow(myds)) {

                    		
                  

                  

                    64
                    !
                    
                      
                fail(paste("Patients with more than one study discontinuation records. "),

                    		
                  

                  

                    65
                    !
                    
                      
                     myrecs)

                    		
                  

                  

                    66
                    
                    
                      
            }

                    		
                  

                  

                    67
                    
                    
                      
        }

                    		
                  

                  

                    68
                    
                    
                      
    }

                    		
                  

                  

                    69
                    
                    
                      
}

            pass()

                    5x

                    2x

    else {

        #Apply company specific preprocessing function

                    3x

                    3x

                    3x

check_ds_sc_strat <- function(DS, SC) {

                    		
                  

                  

                    58
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    59
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    60
                    3x
                    
                      
    if (DS %lacks_any% c("USUBJID", "DSDECOD", "DSSTDTC")) {

                    		
                  

                  

                    61
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    62
                    !

                    64

                    65
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    66
                    3x
                    
                      
    else if (SC %lacks_any% c("USUBJID", "SCTEST", "SCTESTCD", "SCCAT", "SCORRES")) {

                    		
                  

                  

                    67
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    68
                    !
                    
                      
        fail(lacks_msg(SC, c("USUBJID","SCTEST","SCTESTCD","SCCAT","SCORRES")))

                    		
                  

                  

                    69
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    70
                    
                    
                      
    }

                    		
                  

                  

                    71
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    72
                    
                    
                      
    else {

                    		
                  

                  

                    73
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    74
                    3x
                    
                      
        DS = DS %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    75
                    3x
                    
                      
            filter(toupper(DSDECOD) %in% c("RANDOMIZED", "RANDOMIZATION")) %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    76
                    3x
                    
                      
            mutate(DS_RANDDT = as.Date(DSSTDTC)) %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    77
                    3x

                    3x

                    3x

                    82
                    3x

                    3x

                    3x

                    87
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    88

            }

                    		
                  

                  

                    111
                    
                    
                      
        }

                    3x

check_oe_sc_lat_count_fingers <- function(OE, SC) {

                    		
                  

                  

                    115
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    116
                    5x
                    
                      
    if (SC %lacks_any% c("USUBJID", "SCTEST", "SCTESTCD", "SCCAT", "SCORRES", "SCDTC")) {

                    		
                  

                  

                    117
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    118
                    1x
                    
                      
        fail(lacks_msg(SC, c("USUBJID","SCTEST","SCTESTCD","SCCAT","SCORRES", "SCDTC")))

                    		
                  

                  

                    119
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    120
                    
                    
                      
    }

                    		
                  

                  

                    121
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    122
                    4x
                    
                      
    else if (OE %lacks_any% c("USUBJID", "OECAT", "OELAT", "VISIT", "OEDTC",  "OETEST")) {

                    		
                  

                  

                    123
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    124
                    1x
                    
                      
        fail(lacks_msg(OE, c("USUBJID",  "OECAT", "OELAT", "VISIT", "OEDTC", "OETEST")))

                    		
                  

                  

                    125
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    126
                    
                    
                      
    }

                    		
                  

                  

                    127
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    128
                    3x
                    
                      
    else if (OE %>% filter( OECAT == "SAFETY ASSESSMENT OF LOW VISION" & toupper(OELOC) == "EYE" & toupper(OELAT) %in% c("LEFT", "RIGHT")) %>% nrow() == 0){

                    		
                  

                  

                    129
                    !
                    
                      
        pass()

                    		
                  

                  

                    130
                    
                    
                      
    }

                    		
                  

                  

                    131
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    132
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    133
                    
                    
                      
    else {

                    		
                  

                  

                    134
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    135
                    
                    
                      
        # Subset SC data on SC.SCCAT = "STUDY EYE SELECTION", and  and SCTESTCD = "FOCID". SC.SCORRES OS (oculus sinister) means the left

                    		
                  

                  

                    136
                    
                    
                      
        #       eye and OD (oculus dextrus) means the right eye.

                    		
                  

                  

                    137
                    3x
                    
                      
        SC <- SC %>% select(USUBJID, SCTESTCD, SCTEST, SCCAT, SCORRES, SCDTC) %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    138
                    3x
                    
                      
            filter(SCTESTCD %in% c("FOCID")) %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    139
                    3x
                    
                      
            mutate(SC_STUDYEYE = ifelse(SCORRES == "OS", "LEFT",

                    		
                  

                  

                    140
                    3x
                    
                      
                                ifelse(SCORRES == "OD", "RIGHT", "SCORRES Value not OS or OD")))

                    		
                  

                  

                    141
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    142
                    
                    
                      
        # Remove OESTAT NOT DONE

                    		
                  

                  

                    143
                    3x

                    144
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    145
                    1x

                    146
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    147
                    
                    
                      
        }

                    		
                  

                  

                    148
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    149

                    150
                    
                    
                      
        #int_var <- intersect(names(OE), perm_var)

                    		
                  

                  

                    151
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    152
                    3x
                    
                      
        my_select_var <- c("USUBJID", "OELOC", "OECAT", "OELAT", "VISIT", "OEDTC", "OETEST")

                    		
                  

                  

                    153
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    154
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    155

                    156
                    3x
                    
                      
        OE <- OE[, my_select_var]

                    		
                  

                  

                    157
                    3x
                    
                      
        OE <- OE %>% filter(toupper(OECAT) == "SAFETY ASSESSMENT OF LOW VISION" & toupper(OELOC) == "EYE" & toupper(OELAT) %in% c("LEFT", "RIGHT") ) # Remove Missing OELAT

                    		
                  

                  

                    158
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    159

                    160
                    3x
                    
                      
        mydf1 <- left_join(SC, OE, by="USUBJID") %>%

                    		
                  

                  

                    161
                    3x
                    
                      
            mutate(MISFLAG = ifelse((toupper(SC_STUDYEYE) != toupper(OELAT)) | is.na(toupper(OELAT)), 1, 0))

                    		
                  

                  

                    162
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    163
                    3x
                    
                      
        mydf = mydf1 %>% filter(MISFLAG == 1) %>% select(-MISFLAG, -SCTESTCD, -SCTEST, -SCCAT, -SCORRES, -OELOC, -OECAT)

                    		
                  

                  

                    164
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    165
                    3x
                    
                      
        if ((nrow(mydf) > 0 ) == FALSE) {

                    		
                  

                  

                    166
                    1x
                    
                      
            pass()

                    		
                  

                  

                    167
                    
                    
                      
        } else {

                    		
                  

                  

                    168
                    2x
                    
                      
            fail(paste0(nrow(mydf), " record(s) with Post Treatment Count Fingers - Study Eye laterality does not match with Subject Characteristics Study Eye laterality. "), mydf )

                    		
                  

                  

                    169
                    
                    
                      
        }

                    		
                  

                  

                    170
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    171
                    
                    
                      
    }

                    		
                  

                  

                    172

                    48
                    
                    
                      
    ###First check that required variables exist and return a message if they don't

            pass()

        } else {
